{"questionId": 1823, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "\u00c0 partir de quand un versement Multi Vie rapporte-t-il des int\u00e9r\u00eats ?", "titleReword": "dur\u00e9e rendement, dur\u00e9e int\u00e9r\u00eats", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 148, "name": "assurance-vie-148", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "assurance-vie"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2156, "body": "\"Un versement sur le livret (contrat) d'assurance vie \\\"Multi-Vie\\\" prend valeur le jour ouvr\u00e9 Bourse (hors jours f\u00e9ri\u00e9s) suivant la date de remise \u00e0 l'encaissement du ch\u00e8que ou de la date de r\u00e9ception de la demande de pr\u00e9l\u00e8vement \u00e0 Mutavie.  Cette date sert de point de d\u00e9part pour le calcul des int\u00e9r\u00eats. Ceux-ci commencent \u00e0 \u00eatre cr\u00e9dit\u00e9s sur votre contrat d\u00e8s le lendemain.  Avec l'assurance vie Multi Vie (sur le support euros), votre argent rapporte des int\u00e9r\u00eats chaque jour.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 148, "name": "assurance-vie-148", "title": "Mon assurance vie", "slug": "assurance-vie", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "a-partir-quand-versement-multi-vie-rapporte-t-il-interets"}
