{"questionId": 2061, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment recevoir \u00e0 nouveau le code confidentiel pour la carte pr\u00e9pay\u00e9e ?", "titleReword": "perte code, oubli code, perdu code", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 278, "name": "billetterie-278", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "billetterie"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2394, "body": "\"Le code confidentiel de la carte rechargeable peut vous \u00eatre r\u00e9exp\u00e9di\u00e9 \u00e0 votre demande en utilisant le formulaire pr\u00e9vu \u00e0 cet effet dans l'espace de gestion depuis macif.fr. Il est \u00e9galement possible de le recevoir par SMS en envoyant \u00ab PIN \u00bb suivi des 8 derniers chiffres de la carte pr\u00e9pay\u00e9e, au 06 44 63 12 44.  La r\u00e9exp\u00e9dition du code confidentiel est factur\u00e9e 2\u20ac.  Pour l\u2019utilisation du SMS, des frais additionnels de 0,10 \u20ac sont appliqu\u00e9s hors co\u00fbt op\u00e9rateur.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 278, "name": "billetterie-278", "title": "La billetterie", "slug": "billetterie", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "title": "Macif Avantages", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-recevoir-nouveau-code-confidentiel-la-carte-prepayee"}
