{"questionId": 2504, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Quelles sont les conditions d\u2019utilisation de ma E-carte cadeau Zalando ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 62, "name": "associations-cse-62", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 305, "name": "activites-305", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "activites"}, {"filterId": 306, "name": "biens-locaux-306", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "biens-locaux"}, {"filterId": 307, "name": "vehicules-307", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "vehicules"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2837, "body": "\"La E-carte cadeau Zalando est illimit\u00e9e dans le temps. Les E-cartes cadeaux Zalando sont bien cumulables entre elles et utilisables en une ou plusieurs fois dans la limite de sa valeur et peuvent \u00eatre \u00e9ventuellement compl\u00e9t\u00e9e par un autre moyen de paiement.  La E-Carte Cadeau n\u2019est ni \u00e9changeable ni remboursable.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 305, "name": "activites-305", "title": "Activit\u00e9s", "slug": "activites", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 306, "name": "biens-locaux-306", "title": "Biens et locaux", "slug": "biens-locaux", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 307, "name": "vehicules-307", "title": "V\u00e9hicules", "slug": "vehicules", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 62, "name": "associations-cse-62", "title": "Associations - CSE", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "sont-conditions-dutilisation-ma-e-carte-cadeau-zalando"}
