{"questionId": 1978, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment le taux de calcul de la retraite est calcul\u00e9 ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 228, "name": "expedia-228", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "expedia"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2311, "body": "\"Le taux de calcul de la retraite d\u00e9pend de l\u2019\u00e2ge et  du nombre de trimestres acquis, tous r\u00e9gimes confondus. Si l\u2019assur\u00e9 a la dur\u00e9e d\u2019assurance suffisante, la retraite sera calcul\u00e9e \u00e0 taux plein ou \u00ab maximum \u00bb. En revanche, une d\u00e9cote (ou minoration) est appliqu\u00e9e si l'assur\u00e9 n'a pas la dur\u00e9e d\u2019assurance attendue. Le coefficient de minoration d\u00e9pend de l'ann\u00e9e de naissance.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 228, "name": "expedia-228", "title": "Expedia", "slug": "expedia", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "title": "Macif Avantages", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-taux-calcul-retraite-calcule"}
