{"questionId": 2478, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Quelle est la diff\u00e9rence entre l\u2019\u00e2ge l\u00e9gal de d\u00e9part \u00e0 la retraite et l\u2019\u00e2ge de retraite \u00e0 taux plein ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 160, "name": "livret-epargne-populaire-160", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "livret-epargne-populaire"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2811, "body": "\"\u2022L'\u00e2ge l\u00e9gal de d\u00e9part en retraite correspond \u00e0 l'\u00e2ge minimum \u00e0 partir duquel vous pouvez demander votre retraite. Cet \u00e2ge l\u00e9gal est fix\u00e9 \u00e0 62 ans. Des d\u00e9parts avant cet \u00e2ge (appel\u00e9s \u00ab d\u00e9parts anticip\u00e9s \u00bb) sont toutefois possibles, sous certaines conditions.  \u2022L'\u00e2ge \u00e0 taux plein correspond \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e2ge \u00e0 partir duquel la pension de retraite ne sera pas minor\u00e9e. Vous b\u00e9n\u00e9ficierez donc d'une retraite \u00e0 100%.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 160, "name": "livret-epargne-populaire-160", "title": "Livret d'Epargne Populaire", "slug": "livret-epargne-populaire", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "est-difference-entre-lage-legal-depart-la-retraite-lage-retraite-taux-plein"}
