{"questionId": 2596, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Qu'est-ce qu'un virement SEPA ?", "titleReword": "virement europe", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 146, "name": "banque-quotidien-146", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "banque-quotidien"}, {"filterId": 181, "name": "questions-generales-181", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "questions-generales-181"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2929, "body": "\"C\u2019est un virement en euros qui permet de transf\u00e9rer des fonds aussi bien en France que dans l\u2019ensemble des pays de l\u2019espace SEPA. Le virement SEPA remplace le virement national propre \u00e0 chaque pays et le virement transfrontalier entre les pays de l\u2019espace SEPA. Il fait l\u2019objet d\u2019un traitement rapide et fiable, enti\u00e8rement automatis\u00e9.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 146, "name": "banque-quotidien-146", "title": "Banque au quotidien", "slug": "banque-quotidien", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 181, "name": "questions-generales-181", "title": "Questions g\u00e9n\u00e9rales", "slug": "questions-generales-181", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "est-ce-un-virement-sepa"}
