{"questionId": 1894, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment changer un CE en CSE ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 146, "name": "banque-quotidien-146", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "banque-quotidien"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2227, "body": "\"Le CSE doit \u00eatre mis en place \u00e0 la date des \u00e9lections professionnelles dans l\u2019entreprise et dans tous les cas au plus tard au 1er janvier 2020.<br\\/> En savoir plus<br\\/> Concernant votre contrat d'assurance Macif, vos garanties restent inchang\u00e9es.<br\\/>A l\u2019issue de votre passage en CSE, il sera utile de nous le signaler afin de mettre \u00e0 jour les informations de votre contrat.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 146, "name": "banque-quotidien-146", "title": "Banque au quotidien", "slug": "banque-quotidien", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-changer-ce-cse"}
