{"questionId": 2635, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Suis-je assur\u00e9(e) pour mes instruments de musique ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 181, "name": "questions-generales-181", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "questions-generales-181"}, {"filterId": 182, "name": "contrat-182", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "contrat-182"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2968, "body": "\"Gr\u00e2ce au contrat Habitation de la Macif, je peux souscritre une option* qui permet de couvrir, en tout lieu, les instruments de tous les occupants du logement en cas de vol, d'incendie ou de casse accidentelle. Exemples d'instruments : fl\u00fbte, saxophone, guitare, violon, batterie, xylophone...  La Macif couvre m\u00eame les instruments confi\u00e9s ou lou\u00e9s au soci\u00e9taire. * Option accessible avec la Formule Protectrice et accord\u00e9e dans les conditions et limites du contrat Habitation souscrit\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 181, "name": "questions-generales-181", "title": "Questions g\u00e9n\u00e9rales", "slug": "questions-generales-181", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 182, "name": "contrat-182", "title": "Mon contrat", "slug": "contrat-182", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "suis-je-assure-e-pour-instruments-musique"}
