{"questionId": 2022, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment obtenir un relev\u00e9 d'informations ?", "titleReword": "relev\u00e9 situation, releve infos", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 62, "name": "associations-cse-62", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 309, "name": "activites-309", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "activites-309"}, {"filterId": 310, "name": "biens-locaux-310", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "biens-locaux-310"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2355, "body": "\"Le relev\u00e9 d'informations est un document qui r\u00e9sume vos ant\u00e9c\u00e9dents en tant que conducteur. Il contient notamment :<br\\/> votre coefficient de bonus malus, le nombre de sinistre (responsable ou non), le motif de r\u00e9siliation du pr\u00e9c\u00e9dent contrat. Pour obtenir votre relev\u00e9 d'informations Macif, choisissez simplement le mode de contact qui vous convient :<br\\/> Nous \u00e9crire  gr\u00e2ce au formulaire de contact dans votre Espace personnel, vous d\u00e9placer dans votre point d'accueil le plus proche, ou nous t\u00e9l\u00e9phoner.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 309, "name": "activites-309", "title": "Activit\u00e9s", "slug": "activites-309", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 310, "name": "biens-locaux-310", "title": "Biens et locaux", "slug": "biens-locaux-310", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 62, "name": "associations-cse-62", "title": "Associations - CSE", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-obtenir-releve-dinformations"}
