{"questionId": 1972, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment g\u00e9rer mon autorisation de d\u00e9couvert ?", "titleReword": "augmenter plafond, augmenter d\u00e9couvert, baisser d\u00e9couvert, diminuer d\u00e9couvert", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 181, "name": "questions-generales-181", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "questions-generales-181"}, {"filterId": 182, "name": "contrat-182", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "contrat-182"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2305, "body": "\"Pour demander une modification de votre d\u00e9couvert autoris\u00e9, il suffit :  d'imprimer un formulaire intitul\u00e9 \\\"Demande de modification du d\u00e9couvert autoris\u00e9\\\" (disponible dans le menu Op\u00e9rations -> Autres Op\u00e9rations -> Formulaires),  de le renvoyer rempli et sign\u00e9 \u00e0 Socram Banque 2, rue du 24 F\u00e9vrier CS 90000 79092 Niort Cedex 9, accompagn\u00e9 d'un justificatif de revenus de moins de 3 mois pour tous les titulaires du compte concern\u00e9. Vous pouvez \u00e9galement le t\u00e9l\u00e9charger directement ici.  A r\u00e9ception de votre courrier, votre demande sera \u00e9tudi\u00e9e par nos analystes qui vous confirmeront la modification par courrier.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 181, "name": "questions-generales-181", "title": "Questions g\u00e9n\u00e9rales", "slug": "questions-generales-181", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 182, "name": "contrat-182", "title": "Mon contrat", "slug": "contrat-182", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-gerer-autorisation-decouvert"}
