{"questionId": 1963, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment faire pour changer de v\u00e9hicule sur mon contrat d'assurance ?", "titleReword": "changement voiture, changement v\u00e9hicule, remplacement vehicule, remplacement voiture", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 165, "name": "contrat-165", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "contrat"}, {"filterId": 166, "name": "remboursements-166", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "remboursements"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2296, "body": "\"Vous pouvez modifier le v\u00e9hicule de votre contrat d'assurance automobile sur Internet.<br\\/> Pour cela, nous vous invitons \u00e0 r\u00e9aliser et enregistrer un nouveau devis d\u2019assurance automobile sur votre Espace personnel, pour le v\u00e9hicule \u00e0 assurer. Vous pouvez ensuite remplacer le v\u00e9hicule actuel \\\"Changer de v\u00e9hicule\\\" sur votre contrat par le devis correspondant au nouveau v\u00e9hicule, \u00e0 la date d'effet souhait\u00e9e.<br\\/> Sinon, vous pouvez vous d\u00e9placer dans votre point d'accueil le plus proche ou nous t\u00e9l\u00e9phoner.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 165, "name": "contrat-165", "title": "Mon contrat", "slug": "contrat", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 166, "name": "remboursements-166", "title": "Mes remboursements", "slug": "remboursements", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-faire-changer-vehicule-mon-contrat-assurance"}
