{"questionId": 1971, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment formuler une r\u00e9clamation au sujet de la carte pr\u00e9pay\u00e9e ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 281, "name": "extension-web-macif-avantages-281", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "extension-web-macif-avantages"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2304, "body": "\"Vous pouvez formuler une r\u00e9clamation sur la carte rechargeable : Par e-mail \u00e0 l\u2019adresse carte12-17@macif.fr, Par courrier \u00e0 l\u2019adresse suivante : Carte pr\u00e9pay\u00e9e MACIF \u2013 9 rue des Iris \u2013 CS 50000 BESSINES \u2013 79088 NIORT CEDEX 9 Par t\u00e9l\u00e9phone au 09 72 14 88 68 SERVICE GRATUIT + PRIX APPEL du lundi au vendredi de 9h30 \u00e0 18h - hors jours f\u00e9ri\u00e9s -(appel non surtax\u00e9) Par Chat depuis votre espace de gestion, le samedi de 8h \u00e0 20h.   Pour en savoir plus : Consultez les Conditions g\u00e9n\u00e9rales de vente en vigueur au 22 Mai 2019.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 281, "name": "extension-web-macif-avantages-281", "title": "Extension Web Macif Avantages", "slug": "extension-web-macif-avantages", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "title": "Macif Avantages", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment