{"questionId": 2627, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Suis je assur\u00e9 pour mes canalisations ?", "titleReword": "tout \u00e0 l'\u00e9gout, tuyau, tuyaux, tout \u00e0 l'\u00e9go\u00fbt, fosse sceptique, \u00e9vacuation eau, arriv\u00e9e d'eau", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 164, "name": "garanties-164", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "garanties"}, {"filterId": 183, "name": "sinistres-183", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "sinistres-183"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2960, "body": "\"Si vous avez un contrat Habitation Macif, vos canalisations enterr\u00e9es ou non \u00e0 l\u2019int\u00e9rieur des b\u00e2timents assur\u00e9s sont garanties. Pour \u00eatre couvert en cas de dommages sur vos canalisations ext\u00e9rieures (entre l'habitation et le compteur du service des eaux), choisissez l'option assurance canalisations ext\u00e9rieures (accessible uniquement en formule Protectrice).\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 164, "name": "garanties-164", "title": "Mes garanties", "slug": "garanties", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 183, "name": "sinistres-183", "title": "Mes sinistres", "slug": "sinistres-183", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "je-assure-pour-canalisations"}
