{"questionId": 2071, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment r\u00e9server sur Expedia et recevoir mon remboursement ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 217, "name": "campeole-217", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "campeole"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2404, "body": "\"Pour effectuer ma r\u00e9servation d\u2019h\u00f4tel sur Expedia et b\u00e9n\u00e9ficier de mon remboursement :   Je d\u00e9sactive mes bloqueurs de publicit\u00e9s install\u00e9s sur mon navigateur internet. Je vais sur le site www.macifavantages.fr puis je clique sur la page de l'offre Expedia.  Sur la page de pr\u00e9sentation de notre partenariat, je clique sur \\\"J'en profite\\\" et je me laisse guider.  Je clique sur le lien \u201cJe r\u00e9serve\u201d, pour chaque r\u00e9servation. Je re\u00e7ois un email (sous 48h) m\u2019invitant \u00e0 saisir mes coordonn\u00e9es bancaires pour effectuer ma demande de remboursement.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 217, "name": "campeole-217", "title": "Camp\u00e9ole", "slug": "campeole", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "title": "Macif Avantages", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-reserver-expedia-recevoir-remboursement"}
