{"questionId": 1990, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment mensualiser mon paiement ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 147, "name": "carte-prepayee-12-17-147", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "carte-prepayee-12-17"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2323, "body": "\"Vous souhaitez \u00eatre mensualis\u00e9 pour votre cotisation d'assurance ? Pour vos contrats en cours, il vous suffit d'en faire la demande :  \u2022soit dans votre Espace personnel,  \u2022soit en vous d\u00e9pla\u00e7ant dans votre point d'accueil le plus proche de chez vous,  \u2022soit en nous t\u00e9l\u00e9phonant.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 147, "name": "carte-prepayee-12-17-147", "title": "Carte pr\u00e9pay\u00e9e 12/17", "slug": "carte-prepayee-12-17", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-mensualiser-paiement-1990"}
