{"questionId": 2148, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment souscrire une assurance habitation ?", "titleReword": "assurer ma maison", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 280, "name": "carte-digitale-macif-avantages-280", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "carte-digitale-macif-avantages"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2481, "body": "\"Pour souscrire une assurance habitation, faites d'abord un devis et renseignez notamment : le nombre de pi\u00e8ces, la surface \u00e0 assurer.<br\\/> Enregistrez le devis d'assurance habitation dans votre Espace personnel puis cliquez sur \u00ab Souscrire \u00bb. La souscription est simple et rapide en seulement en quelques minutes. Si aucune proposition n'est enregistr\u00e9e dans votre Espace, cliquez sur \\\"R\u00e9aliser un nouveau devis habitation\\\" en prenant de soin de renseigner des donn\u00e9es exactes car celles-ci peuvent sensiblement modifier le tarif et les garanties propos\u00e9es.<br\\/>\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 280, "name": "carte-digitale-macif-avantages-280", "title": "Carte digitale Macif Avantages", "slug": "carte-digitale-macif-avantages", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "title": "Macif Avantages", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-souscrire-assurance-habitation"}
