{"questionId": 2019, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment obtenir un devis Macif Pann'Auto ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 174, "name": "contrat-174", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "contrat-174"}, {"filterId": 176, "name": "attestations-176", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "attestations"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2352, "body": "\"Pour obtenir un devis Macif Pann'Auto, pensez \u00e0 vous munir de quelques informations : immatriculation, date de mise en circulation et kilom\u00e9trage de votre v\u00e9hicule.  Puis, en quelques minutes sur notre site, r\u00e9alisez un devis Macif Pann'Auto en ligne et obtenez notre meilleur tarif pour votre v\u00e9hicule !\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 174, "name": "contrat-174", "title": "Mon contrat", "slug": "contrat-174", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 176, "name": "attestations-176", "title": "Mes attestations", "slug": "attestations", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-obtenir-devis-macif-pannauto"}
