{"questionId": 1957, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment et quand la r\u00e9forme 100% sera-t-elle appliqu\u00e9e ?", "titleReword": "r\u00e9forme mutuelle", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 146, "name": "banque-quotidien-146", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "banque-quotidien"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2290, "body": "\"Votre contrat sant\u00e9 d\u2019entreprise int\u00e9grera l\u2019offre 100% sant\u00e9 avec effet au 1er janvier 2020. La r\u00e9forme \u00e9tant progressive, l\u2019ensemble du dispositif 100% sant\u00e9 sera d\u00e9ploy\u00e9 jusqu\u2019en 2021.  Votre conseiller sp\u00e9cialis\u00e9 est \u00e0 m\u00eame de r\u00e9pondre \u00e0 toutes vos questions, n\u2019h\u00e9sitez pas \u00e0 le contacter.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 146, "name": "banque-quotidien-146", "title": "Banque au quotidien", "slug": "banque-quotidien", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-quand-reforme-100-sera-t-elle-appliquee"}
