{"questionId": 2616, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Qui sont mes d\u00e9l\u00e9gu\u00e9s et comment sont-ils \u00e9lus ?", "titleReword": "\u00e9lections, \u00e9lection, elire", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 197, "name": "delegues-197", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "delegues"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2949, "body": "\"Mes d\u00e9l\u00e9gu\u00e9s sont des soci\u00e9taires Macif ou des adh\u00e9rents Macif-Mutualit\u00e9, comme moi. Ils se portent volontaires aupr\u00e8s de la Macif pour devenir candidat, se pr\u00e9sentent sous forme de liste d\u2019union et sont \u00e9lus au suffrage direct par les soci\u00e9taires (scrutin Macif) ou les adh\u00e9rents (scrutin Macif-Mutualit\u00e9), via un scrutin de liste majoritaire.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 197, "name": "delegues-197", "title": "Les d\u00e9l\u00e9gu\u00e9s", "slug": "delegues", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "mes-delegues-comment-sont-ils-elus"}
