{"questionId": 2030, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment obtenir une attestation de non prise en charge par l'assureur protection juridique ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 211, "name": "adidas-211", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "adidas"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2363, "body": "\"Selon le montant de vos ressources, vous pouvez b\u00e9n\u00e9ficier d'une aide financi\u00e8re de l'Etat, appel\u00e9e aide juridictionnelle qui couvre tout ou partie de vos frais de proc\u00e9dure. Pour cela, il faut justifier de l\u2019absence d\u2019intervention d\u2019un assureur protection juridique. Sur simple demande dans votre Espace assurance, la Macif vous d\u00e9livre une attestation.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 211, "name": "adidas-211", "title": "Adidas", "slug": "adidas", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "title": "Macif Avantages", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-obtenir-attestation-non-prise-charge-lassureur-protection-juridique-2030"}
