{"questionId": 1913, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment consulter mes contrats ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 199, "name": "espace-personnel-199", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "espace-personnel"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2246, "body": "\"Vous pouvez \u00e0 tout moment consulter vos contrats dans \\\"Mes contrats\\\" dans votre \\\"Espace Assurance\\\". Par ce biais, vous pourrez \u00e9galement :  \u2022t\u00e9l\u00e9charger vos conditions g\u00e9n\u00e9rales,  \u2022consulter vos conditions particuli\u00e8res (ces derni\u00e8res vous sont \u00e9galement adress\u00e9es par courrier \u00e0 chaque avenant ou ajout de contrat).\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 199, "name": "espace-personnel-199", "title": "Mon espace personnel", "slug": "espace-personnel", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-consulter-contrats-1913"}
