{"questionId": 1914, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment consulter mes devis d'assurance ?", "titleReword": "voir devis, consulter devis, consultation devis", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 146, "name": "banque-quotidien-146", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "banque-quotidien"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2247, "body": "\"Retrouvez l'ensemble de vos devis m\u00e9moris\u00e9s (assurance auto, habitation, deux-roues, sant\u00e9...) dans votre Espace personnel, \u00e0 la rubrique \\\"Mes devis\\\".<br\\/> Une fois connect\u00e9, vous pouvez : obtenir le d\u00e9tail du devis qui vous int\u00e9resse, modifier ses garanties et options, le supprimer de votre liste, le concr\u00e9tiser \u00e0 la date \u00e0 laquelle vous d\u00e9sirez souscrire le contrat.<br\\/> <br\\/> Puis, apr\u00e8s vous \u00eatre identifi\u00e9 :<br\\/>\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 146, "name": "banque-quotidien-146", "title": "Banque au quotidien", "slug": "banque-quotidien", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-consulter-devis-assurance"}
