{"questionId": 1847, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "C'est quoi le 3DS ?", "titleReword": "paiement s\u00e9curis\u00e9", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 146, "name": "banque-quotidien-146", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "banque-quotidien"}, {"filterId": 181, "name": "questions-generales-181", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "questions-generales-181"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2180, "body": "\"Le programme 3 D Secure est un dispositif de s\u00e9curit\u00e9 (appel\u00e9 Verified by Visa chez Visa et MasterCard Secure Code chez MasterCard) qui a pour but de s\u2019assurer lors d\u2019un paiement en ligne, que le propri\u00e9taire de la carte est bien \u00e0 l\u2019origine de la transaction.  Il s\u2019agit d\u2019un niveau de s\u00e9curit\u00e9 suppl\u00e9mentaire dans le cadre d\u2019op\u00e9rations bancaires effectu\u00e9es \u00e0 distance.  Le principe est simple : au moment de r\u00e9gler l\u2019achat et apr\u00e8s avoir renseign\u00e9 le n\u00b0 de votre carte bancaire Macif, la date d\u2019expiration et le cryptogramme, vous serez dirig\u00e9 vers une page de votre site bancaire o\u00f9 il vous sera r\u00e9clam\u00e9 le code d\u2019authentification non r\u00e9utilisable. Apr\u00e8s saisie du code et validation, vous serez renvoy\u00e9 vers le site de l\u2019e-commer\u00e7ant qui confirmera votre paiement.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 146, "name": "banque-quotidien-146", "title": "Banque au quotidien", "slug": "banque-quotidien", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 181, "name": "questions-generales-181", "title": "Questions g\u00e9n\u00e9rales", "slug": "questions-generales-181", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "quoi-3ds"}
