{"questionId": 2259, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "La banque a-t-elle le droit de changer le taux d'int\u00e9r\u00eat de mon cr\u00e9dit ou de me faire payer des frais ?", "titleReword": "loi lagarde", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 56, "name": "professionnels-56", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 184, "name": "assurance-emprunteur-184", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "assurance-emprunteur"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2592, "body": "\"La banque pr\u00eateuse n\u2019a pas le droit de modifier les conditions du cr\u00e9dit (en particulier son taux) ni de vous r\u00e9clamer des frais suppl\u00e9mentaires en \u00e9change de son acceptation d\u2019un contrat d'assurance emprunteur externe. La loi Lagarde interdit aux banques de p\u00e9naliser les emprunteurs de choisir une assurance externe en jouant sur le taux d\u2019int\u00e9r\u00eat ou en faisant payer des frais de dossiers.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 184, "name": "assurance-emprunteur-184", "title": "Assurance emprunteur", "slug": "assurance-emprunteur", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 56, "name": "professionnels-56", "title": "Professionnels", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "banque-le-droit-changer-taux-interet-mon-credit-de-faire-payer-frais"}
