{"questionId": 2182, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Est ce que les indemnit\u00e9s journali\u00e8res per\u00e7ues sont imposables ?", "titleReword": "indemnit\u00e9s journali\u00e8res, contrat de pr\u00e9voyance, allocation, d\u00e9dommagement, compensation", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 191, "name": "garantie-deces-191", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "garantie-deces"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2515, "body": "\"Les indemnit\u00e9s journali\u00e8res per\u00e7ues en ex\u00e9cution d'un contrat de pr\u00e9voyance sont exon\u00e9r\u00e9es d'imp\u00f4ts, si elles viennent en compl\u00e9ment des prestations de la S\u00e9curit\u00e9 sociale. A l\u2019inverse, les travailleurs non salari\u00e9s b\u00e9n\u00e9ficiant de la Loi Madelin doivent d\u00e9clarer leurs indemnit\u00e9s journali\u00e8res.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 191, "name": "garantie-deces-191", "title": "Garantie d\u00e9c\u00e8s", "slug": "garantie-deces", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "ce-les-indemnites-journalieres-percues-imposables"}
