{"questionId": 2160, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment utiliser mon ch\u00e8que ACS ?", "titleReword": "ch\u00e8que ACS, Aide \u00e0 la compl\u00e9mentaire sant\u00e9, Ch\u00e8que compl\u00e9mentaire sant\u00e9 solidaire", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 150, "name": "credit-auto-150", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-auto"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2493, "body": "\"Si vous \u00eates b\u00e9n\u00e9ficiaire de l'ACS (Aide \u00e0 la Compl\u00e9mentaire Sant\u00e9), confiez votre ch\u00e8que ACS \u00e0 votre mutuelle au moment de la souscription de votre contrat d'assurance sant\u00e9. Le montant de votre aide annuelle viendra en d\u00e9duction du montant de vos cotisations annuelles. Notez que  le contrat ACS Couleurs Mutuelles, est s\u00e9lectionn\u00e9 par le Minist\u00e8re des Affaires Sociales et de la Sant\u00e9. Renseignez vous aupr\u00e8s de votre conseiller Macif pour souscrire !\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 150, "name": "credit-auto-150", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Auto", "slug": "credit-auto", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-utiliser-cheque-acs"}
