{"questionId": 2281, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Les \u00e9quipements de mon camping-car sont ils garantis ?", "titleReword": "garantie \u00e9quipement camping-car, contrat assurance camping-car, contrat assurance caravane ; \u00e9quipements de s\u00e9rie, accessoires et contenu priv\u00e9 du v\u00e9hicule, formule protectrice camping-car,  formule protectrice caravane", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 197, "name": "delegues-197", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "delegues"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2614, "body": "\"Les \u00e9quipements de s\u00e9rie pr\u00e9vus au catalogue contructeur sont couverts en inclusion par le contrat d'assurance Camping Car.  Les autres \u00e9quipements, qui ne sont pas de s\u00e9rie (ex : appareils \u00e9lectriques, hifi, vid\u00e9o, mat\u00e9riel informatique, antennes, etc.) peuvent \u00eatre couverts gr\u00e2ce \u00e0 l'option \\\"Accessoires et contenu priv\u00e9 du v\u00e9hicule\\\" accessible en formule Protectrice, jusqu'\u00e0 10 000 euros selon le niveau d'option choisi.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 197, "name": "delegues-197", "title": "Les d\u00e9l\u00e9gu\u00e9s", "slug": "delegues", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "les-equipements-mon-camping-car-ils-garantis"}
