{"questionId": 2188, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Est-ce que je peux assurer ma piscine ?", "titleReword": "liner, autoport\u00e9e, autoportee, autoportante, auto port\u00e9e, auto portee, coque, pompe, robot", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 164, "name": "garanties-164", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "garanties"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2521, "body": "\"Pour assurer une piscine, v\u00e9rifiez tout d'abord que vous disposez d'un contrat d'assurance habitation. Ajoutez ensuite l'option \\\"Piscine\\\" pour assurer votre piscine, ses \u00e9quipements et les accessoires fix\u00e9s. Pour les am\u00e9nagements au pourtour de la piscine (terrasse, douche...), une option \\\"Biens ext\u00e9rieurs\\\" peut aussi \u00eatre souscrite.<br\\/> Ces options sont accessibles uniquement en formule \\\"Protectrice\\\" de l'assurance habitation Macif.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 164, "name": "garanties-164", "title": "Mes garanties", "slug": "garanties", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "est-ce-je-peux-assurer-piscine"}
