{"questionId": 1830, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "A quoi correspondent les 100 % de ma garantie ?", "titleReword": "pourcentage remboursement sant\u00e9, tableau de garanties sant\u00e9", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 165, "name": "contrat-165", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "contrat"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2163, "body": "\"Une prise en charge \u00e0 100% (base de remboursement de la S\u00e9curit\u00e9 Sociale) de vos frais de sant\u00e9 signifie que la mutuelle intervient en compl\u00e9ment de la S\u00e9curit\u00e9 Sociale dans la limite du montant de la base de remboursement de S\u00e9curit\u00e9 Sociale.  Si les frais r\u00e9els d\u00e9passent ce tarif, ils ne sont pas rembours\u00e9s (exemple : les d\u00e9passements d\u2019honoraires en cas de consultation m\u00e9dicale). Lorsqu\u2019une mutuelle sant\u00e9 indique un remboursement \u00e0 200%, elle rembourse 2 fois la base de remboursement de la S\u00e9curit\u00e9 Sociale. D\u00e9couvrez les taux de prise en charge de notre contrat d\u2019assurance sant\u00e9 Macif ou consultez vos remboursements si vous \u00eates soci\u00e9taire.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 165, "name": "contrat-165", "title": "Mon contrat", "slug": "contrat", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "a-quoi-correspondent-100-de-garantie"}
