{"questionId": 2035, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment passer ma commande chez Aterno - Offre Pro avec ma remise Macif Avantages Pro ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 56, "name": "professionnels-56", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 289, "name": "hp-pros-289", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "hp-pros"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2368, "body": "\"En tant que professionnel, je peux commander chez Aterno et b\u00e9n\u00e9ficier d'une r\u00e9duction Macif Avantages de 15%, deux moyens sont mis \u00e0 ma disposition :   En t\u00e9l\u00e9phonant exclusivement au 0 800 112 000  En vous connectant sur le site www.macifavantages.fr pour les professionnels puis cliquez sur Aterno. Le bouton \\\"J'en profite\\\" vous envoie sur une fen\u00eatre vous permettant d'obtenir un lien \\\"Demandez votre \u00e9tude d\u2019\u00e9conomie d\u2019\u00e9nergie en ligne\\\". Vous serez ainsi dirig\u00e9 directement vers le site internet de notre partenaire.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 289, "name": "hp-pros-289", "title": "HP Pros", "slug": "hp-pros", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 56, "name": "professionnels-56", "title": "Professionnels", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "title": "Macif Avantages", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-passer-commande-chez-aterno-offre-pro-ma-remise-macif-avantages-pro"}
