{"questionId": 2277, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Le v\u00e9hicule personnel d\u2019un b\u00e9n\u00e9vole, adh\u00e9rent ou repr\u00e9sentant de l\u2019association est-il assur\u00e9 en cas d'utilisation dans le cadre d'une activit\u00e9 de l'association ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 62, "name": "associations-cse-62", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 307, "name": "vehicules-307", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "vehicules"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2610, "body": "\"Si le v\u00e9hicule du b\u00e9n\u00e9vole, de l\u2019adh\u00e9rent ou du repr\u00e9sentant de l\u2019association est assur\u00e9 \u00e0 la Macif, le contrat d\u2019assurance Automobile souscrit \u00e0 titre personnel couvre l\u2019utilisation du v\u00e9hicule pour les besoins de l\u2019association. Dans le cas contraire, nous pouvons \u00e9galement proposer \u00e0 l\u2019association un contrat sp\u00e9cifiquement adapt\u00e9 pour garantir les v\u00e9hicules personnels utilis\u00e9s par vos membres, dans le cadre d\u2019une mission sociale\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 307, "name": "vehicules-307", "title": "V\u00e9hicules", "slug": "vehicules", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 62, "name": "associations-cse-62", "title": "Associations - CSE", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "vehicule-personnel-dun-benevole-adherent-representant-lassociation-assure-en-cas-utilisation-le-cadre-une-activite-de-association"}
