{"questionId": 1851, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Combien peut-on ouvrir de contrats d'assurance-vie ?", "titleReword": "nombre contrats, nombre vie", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 148, "name": "assurance-vie-148", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "assurance-vie"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2184, "body": "\"Vous pouvez ouvrir autant de contrats d'assurance-vie que vous le souhaitez (y compris chez des assureurs diff\u00e9rents). Ainsi, vous pourrez mener \u00e0 bien chacun des projets de votre vie : pr\u00e9parer votre retraite, financer les \u00e9tudes de vos enfants, transmettre un capital, diversifier vos placements ou tout simplement vous constituer une r\u00e9serve d\u2019\u00e9pargne...  Consultez nos nombreuses offres d'\u00e9pargne assurance-vie.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 148, "name": "assurance-vie-148", "title": "Mon assurance vie", "slug": "assurance-vie", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "combien-peut-on-ouvrir-contrats-assurance-vie"}
