{"questionId": 2309, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Mon tarif d\u2019assurance emprunteur peut-il changer en cours de contrat ?", "titleReword": "tarif assurance emprunteur", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 184, "name": "assurance-emprunteur-184", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "assurance-emprunteur"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2642, "body": "\"Non. Le tarif de votre assurance emprunteur est calcul\u00e9 en fonction de votre situation au moment de la souscription. Il est ferme et d\u00e9finitif . Vous n\u2019\u00eates pas oblig\u00e9 de nous signaler un quelconque changement, notamment sur votre \u00e9tat de sant\u00e9.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 184, "name": "assurance-emprunteur-184", "title": "Assurance emprunteur", "slug": "assurance-emprunteur", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "tarif-dassurance-emprunteur-peut-il-changer-cours-contrat"}
