{"questionId": 2463, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Quel est le rendement d\u2019un LEP ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 169, "name": "rac-0-169", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "rac-0"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2796, "body": "\"Avec son taux d'int\u00e9r\u00eat fix\u00e9 \u00e0 1% *, le LEP constitue une solution d\u2019\u00e9pargne attractive par rapport aux livrets traditionnels. Les int\u00e9r\u00eats de votre Livret \u00c9pargne Populaire sont calcul\u00e9s sur deux p\u00e9riodes au cours du mois : la premi\u00e8re fois, du 1er au 15 du mois, la seconde, du 16 au 30 (ou 31) du mois. Exemple : pour une dur\u00e9e d\u2019\u00e9pargne souhait\u00e9e de 5 ans, avec un versement initial de 30 \u20ac et un versement mensuel de 20 \u20ac, votre \u00e9pargne constitu\u00e9e sera de 1262,40 \u20ac, dont 32,40 \u20ac d\u2019int\u00e9r\u00eats cumul\u00e9s.<br\\/> * Taux en vigueur au 05\\/07\\/2020, susceptible d'\u00e9volution.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 169, "name": "rac-0-169", "title": "Rac 0", "slug": "rac-0", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "est-rendement-dun-lep"}
