{"questionId": 2279, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Les accessoires de mon deux roues sont-ils assur\u00e9s ?", "titleReword": "assurance accessoires deux-roues, assurance accessoires scooters, assurance moto, assurance scooter, assurance accessoires moto, assurance combinaison moto, assurance blouson moto, assurance motard, assurance casque moto, assurance gants, assurance bottes", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 194, "name": "loisirs-194", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "loisirs"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2612, "body": "\"Les accessoires de votre moto ou scooter peuvent \u00eatre pris en charge dans le cadre de votre assurance moto ou de votre assurance scooter. Pour cela, choisissez la garantie optionnelle \\\"Accessoires et \u00e9quipement du Motard\\\", accessible en formule Protectrice. Elle prot\u00e8ge, dans les conditions et limites fix\u00e9es au contrat, tout ce qui fait le charme de votre moto : peinture personnalis\u00e9e, \u00e9l\u00e9ments d\u2019enjolivement, d\u2019am\u00e9lioration ou de s\u00e9curit\u00e9\u2026 mais aussi votre combinaison, votre blouson, votre casque, vos gants, vos bottes et cela jusqu\u2019\u00e0 3 000 \u20ac selon l\u2019option choisie.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 194, "name": "loisirs-194", "title": "Mes loisirs", "slug": "loisirs", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "accessoires-mon-deux-roues-assures"}
