{"questionId": 1821, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "A combien s'\u00e9l\u00e8vent les franchises de mon contrat auto ?", "titleReword": "franchise auto", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 173, "name": "garanties-173", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "garanties-173"}, {"filterId": 177, "name": "sinistres-177", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "sinistres"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2154, "body": "\"La franchise d'une assurance auto est la somme qui reste \u00e0 la charge de l'assur\u00e9 lors d'un sinistre, et dont le montant est indiqu\u00e9 dans les conditions particuli\u00e8res. Elle est fixe mais elle peut \u00eatre aussi propotionnelle au montant des dommages avec une valeur minimale et une valeur maximale.  Pour conna\u00eetre les franchises de votre contrat d'assurance voiture, nous vous invitons \u00e0 consulter vos conditions particuli\u00e8res, sur votre espace personnel.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 173, "name": "garanties-173", "title": "Mes garanties", "slug": "garanties-173", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 177, "name": "sinistres-177", "title": "Mes sinistres", "slug": "sinistres", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "a-combien-selevent-franchises-mon-contrat-auto"}
