{"questionId": 2135, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment se passe une demande de cr\u00e9dit par internet ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 164, "name": "garanties-164", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "garanties"}, {"filterId": 185, "name": "protection-juridique-185", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "protection-juridique"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2468, "body": "\"Nous vous proposons de r\u00e9aliser votre demande de cr\u00e9dit par internet en 6 \u00e9tapes. Apr\u00e8s avoir renseign\u00e9 les informations sur votre identit\u00e9, votre situation personnelle et professionnelle et le bien que vous souhaitez acheter, vous choisissez l'assurance de votre cr\u00e9dit puis t\u00e9l\u00e9chargez l'ensemble des pi\u00e8ces justificatives n\u00e9cessaires \u00e0 votre demande.  A l'issue de l'analyse de votre demande, vous n'aurez plus qu'\u00e0 signer \u00e9lectroniquement votre offre de cr\u00e9dit et vous pourrez choisir le mode de versement de vos fonds.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 164, "name": "garanties-164", "title": "Mes garanties", "slug": "garanties", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 185, "name": "protection-juridique-185", "title": "Ma protection juridique", "slug": "protection-juridique", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-passe-demande-credit-internet"}
