{"questionId": 2349, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Pourquoi installer l'Extension Web Macif Avantages ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 281, "name": "extension-web-macif-avantages-281", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "extension-web-macif-avantages"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2682, "body": "\"En installant l'extension, vous \u00eates alert\u00e9 et savez imm\u00e9diatement quelle remise s'applique sur les sites de nos partenaires. Activez ensuite votre remise, en cliquant sur \u00ab Activer votre remise \u00bb. D\u00e9couvrez le code promo du partenaire ou soyez redirig\u00e9s sur le site du Partenaire d\u00e9di\u00e9 aux Soci\u00e9taires Macif selon le cas. Suivez les instructions et b\u00e9n\u00e9ficiez de votre avantage r\u00e9serv\u00e9 aux Soci\u00e9taires Macif et aux ayants droit.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 281, "name": "extension-web-macif-avantages-281", "title": "Extension Web Macif Avantages", "slug": "extension-web-macif-avantages", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "title": "Macif Avantages", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "pourquoi-installer-extension-web-macif-avantages"}
