{"questionId": 2131, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment savoir combien co\u00fbte ma banque ?", "titleReword": "tarif banque", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 150, "name": "credit-auto-150", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-auto"}, {"filterId": 151, "name": "credit-moto-151", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-moto"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2464, "body": "\"Tous les ans et au plus tard avant le 31 janvier, votre banque doit vous envoyer obligatoirement un relev\u00e9 annuel des frais bancaires pour l\u2019ann\u00e9e pr\u00e9c\u00e9dente. A la Macif, une partie des b\u00e9n\u00e9fices vous est revers\u00e9e gr\u00e2ce \u00e0 la r\u00e9mun\u00e9ration de votre compte ainsi qu\u2019au service de reversement sur carte bancaire.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 150, "name": "credit-auto-150", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Auto", "slug": "credit-auto", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 151, "name": "credit-moto-151", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Moto", "slug": "credit-moto", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-savoir-combien-coute-banque"}
