{"questionId": 1896, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment choisir ma dur\u00e9e de location et les km parcourus ?", "titleReword": "dur\u00e9e de location, km lld, kms location", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 146, "name": "banque-quotidien-146", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "banque-quotidien"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2229, "body": "\"La v\u00e9ritable question \u00e0 vous poser avant de choisir la dur\u00e9e et le forfait kilom\u00e9trique de votre contrat est \u00ab comment vais-je utiliser mon v\u00e9hicule ? \u00bb. C\u2019est en effet en grande partie la r\u00e9ponse \u00e0 cette question qui d\u00e9terminera le montant des mensualit\u00e9s de votre LLD.<br\\/>Sachez qu\u2019en r\u00e8gle g\u00e9n\u00e9rale, afin d\u2019optimiser ses mensualit\u00e9s de LLD, il est conseill\u00e9 d\u2019opter pour une dur\u00e9e plus longue, si vous roulez peu ou de mani\u00e8re mod\u00e9r\u00e9e. A l\u2019inverse, si vous roulez \u00e9norm\u00e9ment, il est conseill\u00e9 d\u2019opter pour une dur\u00e9e de LLD plus courte.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 146, "name": "banque-quotidien-146", "title": "Banque au quotidien", "slug": "banque-quotidien", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-choisir-duree-location-les-km-parcourus"}
