{"questionId": 1918, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment consulter mes relev\u00e9s de compte ?", "titleReword": "consultation relev\u00e9", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 146, "name": "banque-quotidien-146", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "banque-quotidien"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2251, "body": "\"En vous connectant \u00e0 votre Espace bancaire, vous pourrez consulter et t\u00e9l\u00e9charger vos relev\u00e9s de compte en vous munissant de votre identifiant et de votre mot de passe pour acc\u00e9der \u00e0 vos comptes en toute s\u00e9curit\u00e9.   Ces deux codes vous ont \u00e9t\u00e9 communiqu\u00e9s par courriers s\u00e9par\u00e9s d\u00e8s l\u2019ouverture de votre compte.  Vos relev\u00e9s de compte restent disponibles sur votre espace durant 10 ans.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 146, "name": "banque-quotidien-146", "title": "Banque au quotidien", "slug": "banque-quotidien", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-consulter-releves-compte"}
