{"questionId": 1903, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment conna\u00eetre mon d\u00e9couvert autoris\u00e9 ?", "titleReword": "d\u00e9passement", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 147, "name": "carte-prepayee-12-17-147", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "carte-prepayee-12-17"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2236, "body": "\"Le montant de votre autorisation de d\u00e9couvert est disponible sur la synth\u00e8se de vos comptes (\u00e0 droite de votre solde), ainsi que sur la premi\u00e8re page de votre relev\u00e9 de compte mensuel.  Il figure \u00e9galement dans les conditions particuli\u00e8res.  Si vous consultez vos comptes depuis votre mobile, cliquez sur \u00ab compte de d\u00e9p\u00f4t \u00bb. Sur l\u2019\u00e9cran suivant, le montant du d\u00e9couvert autoris\u00e9 est affich\u00e9 sous le nom du titulaire.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 147, "name": "carte-prepayee-12-17-147", "title": "Carte pr\u00e9pay\u00e9e 12/17", "slug": "carte-prepayee-12-17", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-connaitre-decouvert-autorise"}
