{"questionId": 2121, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment r\u00e9silier mon contrat d'assurance auto ?", "titleReword": "suspendre auto, r\u00e9silier auto, r\u00e9siliation voiture", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 188, "name": "garantie-accidents-188", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "garantie-accidents"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2454, "body": "\"Suite \u00e0 vente ou destruction, vous pouvez nous transmettre directement en ligne les documents, en vous connectant \u00e0 votre espace personnel, rubrique \\\"Messagerie\\\", et en saisissant votre demande.<br\\/>Pour en savoir plus sur la r\u00e9siliation de votre contrat d'assurance auto, nous vous invitons \u00e0 contacter votre conseiller Macif par t\u00e9l\u00e9phone ou \u00e0 vous rendre \u00e0 l'agence \u00e0 la plus proche de chez vous.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 188, "name": "garantie-accidents-188", "title": "Garantie accidents", "slug": "garantie-accidents", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-resilier-contrat-assurance-auto"}
