{"questionId": 2366, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Proposez-vous une assurance pour couvrir mon cr\u00e9dit \u00e0 la consommation r\u00e9alis\u00e9 par internet ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 150, "name": "credit-auto-150", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-auto"}, {"filterId": 151, "name": "credit-moto-151", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-moto"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2699, "body": "\"La Macif propose une assurance pour ses cr\u00e9dits.  Celle-ci prend en charge le remboursement des mensualit\u00e9s du cr\u00e9dit ou du capital restant d\u00fb en cas de d\u00e9c\u00e8s, de perte totale et irr\u00e9versible d'autonomie, d'incapacit\u00e9 temporaire et totale de travail avec perte de revenus ou d'invalidit\u00e9 permanente.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 150, "name": "credit-auto-150", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Auto", "slug": "credit-auto", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 151, "name": "credit-moto-151", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Moto", "slug": "credit-moto", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "proposez-vous-assurance-couvrir-credit-la-consommation-realise-par-internet"}
