{"questionId": 2125, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment r\u00e9silier mon contrat Garantie Accident ?", "titleReword": "r\u00e9siliation, contrat, pr\u00e9voyance, accident domestique", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 165, "name": "contrat-165", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "contrat"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2458, "body": "\"Votre Garantie Accident (r\u00e9gime de pr\u00e9voyance familiale accident ou RPFA) est un contrat annuel \u00e0 tacite reconduction. Vous pouvez le r\u00e9silier \u00e0 la date d'\u00e9ch\u00e9ance par lettre recommand\u00e9e.  Nous attirons votre attention sur l'importance de ce contrat, qui couvre les cons\u00e9quences financi\u00e8res des accidents auxquels vous et votre famille pouvez \u00eatre confront\u00e9s dans le cadre de votre vie priv\u00e9e (au volant, accidents domestiques, accidents sportifs, etc.)\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 165, "name": "contrat-165", "title": "Mon contrat", "slug": "contrat", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-resilier-contrat-garantie-accident"}
