{"questionId": 2385, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Puis-je pr\u00eater mon scooter ?", "titleReword": "pr\u00eater scooter, pr\u00eater mobylette, pr\u00eate deux roues, scooter, mobylette, deux-roues, franchise pr\u00eater scooter, franchise accident responsable scooter, franchise accident responsable", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 186, "name": "2-roues-186", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "2-roues"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2718, "body": "\"Vous pouvez pr\u00eater votre scooter \u00e0 quelqu'un. Cependant, une franchise sp\u00e9cifique indiqu\u00e9e dans les conditions particuli\u00e8res sera appliqu\u00e9e en cas d\u2019accident responsable (sauf s'il s'agit de votre conjoint, concubin, partenaire pacs\u00e9, ou un membre de la famille vivant sous votre toit pour les 50 cm3).\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 186, "name": "2-roues-186", "title": "Mon 2 roues", "slug": "2-roues", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "puis-je-preter-scooter"}
