{"questionId": 2562, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Qu'est ce que la Taxe Douani\u00e8re ?", "titleReword": "taxe douani\u00e8re, droits et taxes douane, droits caravane, taxe douani\u00e8re caravane, taxe douani\u00e8re camping-car", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 181, "name": "questions-generales-181", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "questions-generales-181"}, {"filterId": 185, "name": "protection-juridique-185", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "protection-juridique"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2895, "body": "\"Dans certains pays (ex : Maroc, Tunisie), le camping cariste qui y entre sur le sol avec son v\u00e9hicule pour un s\u00e9jour touristique doit imp\u00e9rativement quitter le pays avec son v\u00e9hicule. Le cas contraire, il devra s\u2019acquitter des droits et taxes de douane, m\u00eame en cas de vol ou d\u2019accident.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 181, "name": "questions-generales-181", "title": "Questions g\u00e9n\u00e9rales", "slug": "questions-generales-181", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 185, "name": "protection-juridique-185", "title": "Ma protection juridique", "slug": "protection-juridique", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "est-que-taxe-douaniere"}
