{"questionId": 1906, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment conna\u00eetre ou modifier le plafond de la carte bancaire Macif ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 171, "name": "questions-generales-lauto-171", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "questions-generales-lauto"}, {"filterId": 174, "name": "contrat-174", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "contrat-174"}, {"filterId": 182, "name": "contrat-182", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "contrat-182"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2239, "body": "\"Les plafonds de la carte bancaire Macif sont indiqu\u00e9s dans les Conditions g\u00e9n\u00e9rales.  Carte Visa Electron :  Plafond de retrait sur 7 jours : 300 euros Plafond de paiements sur 30 jours : 2 400 euros<br\\/> Carte Visa Classique :   Plafond de retrait sur 7 jours : 300 euros Plafond de paiements sur 30 jours : 2 400 euros <br\\/> Carte Visa Premier :  Plafond de retrait sur 7 jours : 900 euros Plafond de paiements sur 30 jours : 5 000 euros  <br\\/>Pour modifier les plafonds de  votre carte, prenez contact avec un conseiller Macifin' au : N\u00b0 Cristal 09 69 39 49 59 APPEL NON SURTAXE\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 171, "name": "questions-generales-lauto-171", "title": "Questions g\u00e9n\u00e9rales sur l'Auto", "slug": "questions-generales-lauto", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 174, "name": "contrat-174", "title": "Mon contrat", "slug": "contrat-174", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 182, "name": "contrat-182", "title": "Mon contrat", "slug": "contrat-182", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted"