{"questionId": 2650, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Y-a-t-il des frais lors d'un retrait dans un distributeur avec la carte pr\u00e9pay\u00e9e 12-17 ans ?", "titleReword": "frais retrait, tarif retrait", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 147, "name": "carte-prepayee-12-17-147", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "carte-prepayee-12-17"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2983, "body": "\"Les frais de retraits dans les distributeurs automatiques de billets (DAB) de la zone euro sont compris dans la cotisation annuelle de 18 \u20ac.  En revanche, des frais s\u2019appliquent sur les retraits dans les DAB en dehors de la zone euro.  Pour en savoir plus consultez :  le Guide tarifaire au 15 Octobre 2019 les Conditions g\u00e9n\u00e9rales de vente au 22 Mai 2019.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 147, "name": "carte-prepayee-12-17-147", "title": "Carte pr\u00e9pay\u00e9e 12/17", "slug": "carte-prepayee-12-17", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "y-a-t-il-frais-lors-un-retrait-un-distributeur-la-carte-prepayee-12-17-ans"}
