{"questionId": 1956, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment estimer sa pension de retraite ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 165, "name": "contrat-165", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "contrat"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2289, "body": "\"\u00c0 partir de 45 ans, vous pouvez obtenir une estimation de votre future retraite en fonction de diff\u00e9rents crit\u00e8res (hypoth\u00e8ses de carri\u00e8re, \u00e2ge de d\u00e9part, etc.). Les estimations fournies s\u2019appuient sur les donn\u00e9es r\u00e9elles de votre carri\u00e8re connues \u00e0 ce jour par vos r\u00e9gimes de retraite. Pour obtenir cette estimation, connectez-vous \u00e0 votre compte retraite sur le site officiel Info Retraite.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 165, "name": "contrat-165", "title": "Mon contrat", "slug": "contrat", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-estimer-pension-retraite"}
