{"questionId": 1832, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "A quoi sert la convention Aeras ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 150, "name": "credit-auto-150", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-auto"}, {"filterId": 151, "name": "credit-moto-151", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-moto"}, {"filterId": 152, "name": "credit-camping-car-152", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-camping-car"}, {"filterId": 153, "name": "credit-bateau-153", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-bateau"}, {"filterId": 154, "name": "credit-mobil-home-154", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-mobil-home"}, {"filterId": 155, "name": "credit-projet-155", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-projet"}, {"filterId": 156, "name": "credit-travaux-156", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-travaux"}, {"filterId": 157, "name": "credit-jeune-157", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-jeune"}, {"filterId": 158, "name": "credit-developpement-durable-158", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-developpement-durable"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2165, "body": "\"La convention AERAS permet de faciliter l'acc\u00e8s au cr\u00e9dit des personnes pr\u00e9sentant un risque aggrav\u00e9 de sant\u00e9. Lors de l'adh\u00e9sion \u00e0 l'assurance, celle-ci sera simplifi\u00e9e (sans questionnaire de sant\u00e9) si vous remplissez les conditions cumulatives suivantes : le cr\u00e9dit est d'une dur\u00e9e inf\u00e9rieure ou \u00e9gale \u00e0 4 ans, l'emprunteur a 50 ans au plus, le montant du cr\u00e9dit ne d\u00e9passe pas 17000 \u20ac. Pour en savoir plus, consultez le site des pouvoirs publics d\u00e9di\u00e9 \u00e0 la Convention A\u00e9ras.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 150, "name": "credit-auto-150", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Auto", "slug": "credit-auto", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 151, "name": "credit-moto-151", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Moto", "slug": "credit-moto", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 152, "name": "credit-camping-car-152", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Camping-car", "slug": "credit-camping-car", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 153, "name": "credit-bateau-153", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Bateau", "slug": "credit-bateau", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 154, "name": "credit-mobil-home-154", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Mobil-home", "slug": "credit-mobil-home", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 155, "name": "credit-projet-155", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Projet", "slug": "credit-projet", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 156, "name": "credit-travaux-156", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Travaux", "slug": "credit-travaux", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 157, "name": "credit-jeune-157", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Jeune", "slug": "credit-jeune", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 158, "name": "credit-developpement-durable-158", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit D\u00e9veloppement Durable", "slug": "credit-developpement-durable", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "a-quoi-sert-convention-aeras"}
