{"questionId": 2594, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Qu'est-ce qu'un cookie sur Hotels.com et \u00e0 quoi sert-il ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 236, "name": "hotels-com-236", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "hotels-com"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2927, "body": "\"Un cookie est un fichier qui est d\u00e9pos\u00e9 temporairement sur mon ordinateur lorsque je navigue sur Internet. Il est inoffensif. Dans le cas pr\u00e9sent, ce fichier permet \u00e0 Hotels.com de m'identifier comme \u00e9tant soci\u00e9taire Macif. Il est donc indispensable pour pouvoir b\u00e9n\u00e9ficier de ma remise.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 236, "name": "hotels-com-236", "title": "Hotels.com", "slug": "hotels-com", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "title": "Macif Avantages", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "est-ce-un-cookie-hotels-com-et-quoi-sert-il"}
