{"questionId": 2511, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Quelles sont les d\u00e9marches si le CE/CSE/CAS/COS organise une activit\u00e9 sociale ou culturelle ?", "titleReword": "culture", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 228, "name": "expedia-228", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "expedia"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2844, "body": "\"Avec le contrat MultigarantieActivit\u00e9s Sociales CE, vous \u00eates assur\u00e9 dans le cadre des activit\u00e9s sociales, culturelles, festives ou sportives organis\u00e9es par vos soins, sans d\u00e9marche pr\u00e9alable pour la plupart d\u2019entre elles : arbre de No\u00ebl, sorties organis\u00e9es, \u2026<br\\/> Si vous louez une salle dans le cadre de cet \u00e9v\u00e8nement, le contrat Multigarantie Activit\u00e9s Sociales CE en pr\u00e9voit l\u2019assurance sans surco\u00fbt. Cependant, pour certains types de b\u00e2timents (ch\u00e2teaux, manoirs, sites class\u00e9s, b\u00e2timents de prestige\u2026) nous vous invitons \u00e0 nous contacter par t\u00e9l\u00e9phone.<br\\/>Pensez \u00e0 demander une attestation pour le bailleur.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 228, "name": "expedia-228", "title": "Expedia", "slug": "expedia", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "title": "Macif Avantages", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "sont-demarches-si-ce-cse-cas-cos-organise-activite-sociale-culturelle"}
