{"questionId": 1836, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Ai-je droit \u00e0 un v\u00e9hicule de remplacement ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 174, "name": "contrat-174", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "contrat-174"}, {"filterId": 177, "name": "sinistres-177", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "sinistres"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2169, "body": "\"Vous pouvez b\u00e9n\u00e9ficier d'un v\u00e9hicule de remplacement dans les cas suivants :   vol du v\u00e9hicule (dans la limite de 30 jours),  accident (dans la limite de 15 jours),  panne (dans la limite de 7 jours).  Pour obtenir un v\u00e9hicule de remplacement, v\u00e9rifiez tout d\u2019abord que votre contrat d'assurance auto Macif inclut bien cette option appel\u00e9e \\\"Service Mobilit\u00e9\\\". Sinon, vous pouvez la souscrire dans votre Espace Assurance si vous disposez d\u2019une formule Elargie ou Protectrice. Pour la formule Excellence, le v\u00e9hicule de remplacement est automatiquement inclus. Ensuite, contactez notre service Assistance qui s\u2019occupe du reste !\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 174, "name": "contrat-174", "title": "Mon contrat", "slug": "contrat-174", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 177, "name": "sinistres-177", "title": "Mes sinistres", "slug": "sinistres", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "ai-je-droit-un-vehicule-remplacement-1836"}
