{"questionId": 2119, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment r\u00e9silier la carte pr\u00e9pay\u00e9e 12-17 ans ?", "titleReword": "r\u00e9silie carte, r\u00e9silier cb, r\u00e9siliation cb, r\u00e9siliation carte", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 147, "name": "carte-prepayee-12-17-147", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "carte-prepayee-12-17"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2452, "body": "\"Si vous souhaitez r\u00e9silier les Conditions G\u00e9n\u00e9rales li\u00e9es \u00e0 votre carte pr\u00e9pay\u00e9e 12\\/17 ans, vous devrez en faire la demande et demander un remboursement du Solde disponible par courrier \u00e0 l'adresse suivante :  Carte pr\u00e9pay\u00e9e MACIF - 9 rue des Iris - CS50000 Bessines - 79088 Niort cedex 9.  La r\u00e9siliation prendra effet dans un d\u00e9lai maximum de 30 jours apr\u00e8s notification de la demande de r\u00e9siliation.  Nous proc\u00e8derons au remboursement du Solde disponible de la Carte par virement conform\u00e9ment aux Conditions g\u00e9n\u00e9rales.  Consultez les Conditions g\u00e9n\u00e9rales en vigueur au 22 Mai 2019.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 147, "name": "carte-prepayee-12-17-147", "title": "Carte pr\u00e9pay\u00e9e 12/17", "slug": "carte-prepayee-12-17", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": -1, "questionSlug": "comment-resilier-carte-prepayee-12-17-ans"}
