{"questionId": 2619, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Si j'ai des questions, \u00e0 qui m'adresser ?", "titleReword": "questions garantie emprunteur,question garantie emprunteur", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 184, "name": "assurance-emprunteur-184", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "assurance-emprunteur"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2952, "body": "\"La Macif a mis en place une plateforme d\u00e9di\u00e9e au contrat Garantie Emprunteur. Notre \u00e9quipe d'experts de l'assurance emprunteur vous conseille et r\u00e9pond \u00e0 toutes vos questions du lundi au vendredi de 8H \u00e0 20H et le samedi jusqu\u2019\u00e0 17H15. Contactez-les au 04 78 62 16 62 (co\u00fbt selon op\u00e9rateur).\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 184, "name": "assurance-emprunteur-184", "title": "Assurance emprunteur", "slug": "assurance-emprunteur", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "si-ai-questions-a-qui-adresser"}
