{"questionId": 2620, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Si je choisis une formule en capital, sous quel d\u00e9lai le capital sera-t-il vers\u00e9 \u00e0 mes proches ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 192, "name": "garantie-obseques-192", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "garantie-obseques"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2953, "body": "\"En choisissant une assurance obs\u00e8ques en formule capital, le capital garanti est vers\u00e9 \u00e0 vos proches dans un d\u00e9lai maximal de 30 jours. Ce d\u00e9lai court \u00e0 compter de la r\u00e9ception de l\u2019int\u00e9gralit\u00e9 des documents demand\u00e9s par la Mutuelle.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 192, "name": "garantie-obseques-192", "title": "Garantie obs\u00e8ques", "slug": "garantie-obseques", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "si-choisis-formule-capital-sous-delai-capital-sera-t-il-verse-a-mes-proches"}
