{"questionId": 2268, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "L'assistance pour mon v\u00e9hicule est-elle comprise dans toutes les formules ?", "titleReword": "remorquage, d\u00e9pannage, cl\u00e9, crevaison, panne, vandalisme, cl\u00e9s, clef, clefs, incendie, vol, carjacking, car-jacking, ima, carrossier, r\u00e9parateur, garagiste", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 173, "name": "garanties-173", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "garanties-173"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2601, "body": "\"Toutes nos formules d'assurance automobile comprennent l'assistance g\u00e9n\u00e9rale auto. Cela vous donne droit, dans les conditions et limites fix\u00e9es au contrat, \u00e0 un d\u00e9pannage ou remorquage en cas d'accident, mais aussi en cas de panne lorsque celle-ci a lieu \u00e0 plus de 50km du domicile.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 173, "name": "garanties-173", "title": "Mes garanties", "slug": "garanties-173", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 1, "questionSlug": "assistance-mon-vehicule-comprise-toutes-formules"}
