{"questionId": 2176, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Dans quel d\u00e9lai serai-je couvert apr\u00e8s la souscription ?", "titleReword": "d\u00e9lai mutuelle, d\u00e9lai carence", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 165, "name": "contrat-165", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "contrat"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2509, "body": "\"Aucun d\u00e9lai de carence n'est appliqu\u00e9 sur votre contrat de compl\u00e9mentaire sant\u00e9. Avec le contrat Garantie Sant\u00e9, vous b\u00e9n\u00e9ficiez de nos prestations d\u00e8s la date d'effet de vos garanties. Les soins intervenus avant la souscription de votre contrat sant\u00e9 ne seront pas pris en charge.Toutefois, pour les actes d\u2019hospitalisation et les actes r\u00e9alis\u00e9s en s\u00e9rie, commenc\u00e9s avant la date d\u2019effet du contrat, le contrat prendra en charge les soins r\u00e9alis\u00e9s apr\u00e8s la prise d\u2019effet du contrat, sous r\u00e9serve d'une pr\u00e9c\u00e9dente couverture sans interruption d'assurance, conform\u00e9ment aux conditions et limites pr\u00e9vues au contrat.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 165, "name": "contrat-165", "title": "Mon contrat", "slug": "contrat", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "quel-delai-serai-je-couvert-apres-souscription"}
