{"questionId": 2267, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "L'assistance est-elle comprise dans ma formule habitation ?", "titleReword": "inondation, cl\u00e9, crevaison, panne, vandalisme, cl\u00e9s, clef, clefs, incendie, toiture, vol, cambriolage, agression, ima, imatech, plombier, \u00e9lectricien, couvreur", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 164, "name": "garanties-164", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "garanties"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2600, "body": "\"Chaque formule du contrat d'assurance habitation Macif comprend l'assistance g\u00e9n\u00e9rale.  Dans les conditions fix\u00e9es au contrat, une aide est apport\u00e9e imm\u00e9diatement \u00e0 nos assur\u00e9s en cas de sinistre garanti survenu dans son habitation :  vol, vandalisme, incendie, d\u00e9g\u00e2t des eaux, \u00e9v\u00e9nements climatiques, impr\u00e9vu n\u00e9cessitant une intervention urgente (perte de clefs, panne de chauffage...) avec la prise en charge du d\u00e9placement d'un prestataire et de la premi\u00e8re heure de main d'oeuvre.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 164, "name": "garanties-164", "title": "Mes garanties", "slug": "garanties", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 1, "questionSlug": "assistance-comprise-ma-formule-habitation"}
