{"questionId": 2306, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Mon nom appara\u00eet-il sur la carte grise ?", "titleReword": "location longue dur\u00e9e, titulaire carte grise, nom carte grise", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 175, "name": "location-longue-duree-175", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "location-longue-duree"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2639, "body": "\"Avec MACIF C'parti (1) , la carte grise de la voiture est \u00e9tablie au nom du loueur c\u2019est-\u00e0-dire au nom de LeasePlan notre partenaire. Cependant, votre nom appara\u00eet \u00e9galement sur le document, en compl\u00e9ment d\u2019information.<br\\/> (1) L\u2019offre MACIF C\u2019parti est r\u00e9serv\u00e9e aux soci\u00e9taires Macif \u00e9ligibles sous r\u00e9serve d\u2019acceptation par LeasePlan. D\u00e9tails des conditions et limites dans les Conditions g\u00e9n\u00e9rales de location.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 175, "name": "location-longue-duree-175", "title": "Location Longue Dur\u00e9e", "slug": "location-longue-duree", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "nom-apparait-il-carte-grise"}
