{"questionId": 1969, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment fonctionnent les remises de ch\u00e8ques ?", "titleReword": "remise cheque, remise ch\u00e8que", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 146, "name": "banque-quotidien-146", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "banque-quotidien"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2302, "body": "\"Dans tous les cas, pensez \u00e0 inscrire votre N\u00b0 de compte complet et \u00e0 apposer votre signature au dos du ch\u00e8que et \u00e0 le joindre au bordereau rempli et sign\u00e9.   Les ch\u00e8ques dont vous \u00eates b\u00e9n\u00e9ficiaires peuvent \u00eatre remis \u00e0 l\u2019encaissement par envoi postal (affranchissement \u00e0 votre charge) \u00e0 Socram Banque 2 rue du 24 F\u00e9vrier \u2013 CS 90000 \u2013 79092 Niort Cedex 9.   Sinon vous avez la possibilit\u00e9 de les d\u00e9poser dans un point d\u2019accueil Macif (acheminement gratuit).  La date de valeur d\u2019encaissement de votre(s) ch\u00e8que(s) sera le jour J \u00e0 r\u00e9ception chez Socram Banque.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 146, "name": "banque-quotidien-146", "title": "Banque au quotidien", "slug": "banque-quotidien", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-fonctionnent-remises-cheques"}
