{"questionId": 2356, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Prenez-vous en charge l'orthodontie pour les adultes ?", "titleReword": "remboursement orthodontie adulte,", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 164, "name": "garanties-164", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "garanties"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2689, "body": "\"Les soins d'orthodontie adulte (c'est-\u00e0-dire des personnes \u00e2g\u00e9es de plus de 16 ans) ne sont pas pris en charge par notre mutuelle. Dans certains cas exceptionnels, c'est-\u00e0-dire o\u00f9 ces soins seraient pris en charge par la S\u00e9curit\u00e9 sociale, nous interviendrons dans leur remboursement dans les conditions et limites pr\u00e9vues au contrat Garantie Sant\u00e9.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 164, "name": "garanties-164", "title": "Mes garanties", "slug": "garanties", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "prenez-vous-charge-orthodontie-les-adultes"}
