{"questionId": 2180, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "En quoi consiste l'option \"Assistance panne 0 km\" ?", "titleReword": "cl\u00e9, crevaison, panne, vandalisme, cl\u00e9s, clef, clefs, incendie, toiture, vol, agression, batterie, ima, carrossier, r\u00e9parateur, garagiste", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 173, "name": "garanties-173", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "garanties-173"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2513, "body": "\"L'option \\\"Assistance Panne 0 km\\\", accessible dans plusieurs formules, vous donne droit, dans les conditions et limites fix\u00e9es au contrat, \u00e0 une aide en cas de panne de votre v\u00e9hicule (panne m\u00e9canique, panne de carburant, crevaison), m\u00eame \u00e0 moins de 50 kms de votre domicile. Cette option vient en compl\u00e9ment des prestations accord\u00e9es dans le cadre de l\u2019assistance g\u00e9n\u00e9rale (assistance au v\u00e9hicule).<br\\/> Sachez que cette option \\\"Assistance panne 0 km\\\"peut \u00eatre souscrite en ligne en quelques clic. Elle est automatiquement incluse dans la formule Excellence du contrat Auto.<br\\/> En savoir plus : consultez le tableau des garanties du contrat d'assurance auto\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 173, "name": "garanties-173", "title": "Mes garanties", "slug": "garanties-173", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 1, "questionSlug": "quoi-consiste-option-assistance-panne-0-km"}
