{"questionId": 2007, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment obtenir des infos sur ma r\u00e9servation de vacances faite via Macif Avantages ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 165, "name": "contrat-165", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "contrat"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2340, "body": "\"Macif Avantages n\u2019intervient pas dans la gestion des r\u00e9servations effectu\u00e9es aupr\u00e8s d'un voyagiste. Pour tout renseignement relatif \u00e0 votre r\u00e9servation (suivi, carnet de voyages, billet, confirmation,\u2026), nous vous invitons \u00e0 le contacter directement sur la ligne d\u00e9di\u00e9e indiqu\u00e9e dans notre annonce.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 165, "name": "contrat-165", "title": "Mon contrat", "slug": "contrat", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-obtenir-infos-ma-reservation-vacances-faite-via-macif-avantages"}
