{"questionId": 1849, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Combien co\u00fbte une carte bancaire pr\u00e9pay\u00e9e Mastercard pour les 12-17 ans ?", "titleReword": "tarif carte, tarif cb", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 147, "name": "carte-prepayee-12-17-147", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "carte-prepayee-12-17"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2182, "body": "\"La cotisation de la carte pr\u00e9pay\u00e9e est de 18 \u20ac* par an et devra \u00eatre acquitt\u00e9e chaque ann\u00e9e \u00e0 la date anniversaire de la souscription.  Pour en savoir plus : consultez le Guide tarifaire en vigueur. En cas de non-utilisation de la carte pr\u00e9pay\u00e9e, aucuns frais ne s\u2019appliquent, except\u00e9 la cotisation annuelle de 18 \u20ac \u00e0 la date anniversaire de la souscription de la carte bancaire rechargeable.<br\\/> *Tarif en vigueur au 15\\/10\\/2019, susceptible d'\u00e9volution \u00e0 tout moment. Voir guide tarifaire en vigueur au jour de la souscription de la carte.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 147, "name": "carte-prepayee-12-17-147", "title": "Carte pr\u00e9pay\u00e9e 12/17", "slug": "carte-prepayee-12-17", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "combien-coute-carte-bancaire-prepayee-mastercard-les-12-17-ans"}
