{"questionId": 1951, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment envoyer ma candidature au groupe Macif ?", "titleReword": "candidature, postuler, poste, offre d'emploi, emploi, job", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 188, "name": "garantie-accidents-188", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "garantie-accidents"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2284, "body": "\"Pour postuler et rejoindre le Groupe Macif, d\u00e9posez votre candidature spontan\u00e9e ou votre r\u00e9ponse \u00e0 une offre, directement en ligne.  Indiquez l'(es) entit\u00e9(s) concern\u00e9e(s), r\u00e9gion, filiale, si\u00e8ge... Le site transmettra \u00e0 (aux) l'entit\u00e9(s) concern\u00e9e(s).  A tout d\u00e9p\u00f4t de candidature, une r\u00e9ponse syst\u00e9matique instantan\u00e9e est faite \u00e0 l'internaute, pr\u00e9cisant que sans r\u00e9ponse de la DRH d'entit\u00e9 concern\u00e9e dans un d\u00e9lai de deux mois, l'internaute peut consid\u00e9rer que sa canditature n'est pas retenue.  Consultez toutes nos offres d'emploi en assurance !\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 188, "name": "garantie-accidents-188", "title": "Garantie accidents", "slug": "garantie-accidents", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-envoyer-candidature-groupe-macif"}
