{"questionId": 2407, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Quand connait-on les taux servis sur vos contrats d'\u00e9pargne assurance-vie ?", "titleReword": "taux \u00e9pargne, taux mutlivie, taux multi vie", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 150, "name": "credit-auto-150", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-auto"}, {"filterId": 151, "name": "credit-moto-151", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-moto"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2740, "body": "\"Sur le support en euros de nos contrats d'assurance-vie, un taux d'int\u00e9r\u00eat minimum vous est garanti chaque ann\u00e9e, auquel s'ajoutent \u00e9ventuellement des int\u00e9r\u00eats compl\u00e9mentaires en fin d'ann\u00e9e. Le taux de rendement des contrats sur l'ann\u00e9e \u00e9coul\u00e9e est connu d\u00e9but janvier.  Vous pourrez les retrouver sur la page \\\"Assurance-vie - Multi Vie\\\".\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 150, "name": "credit-auto-150", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Auto", "slug": "credit-auto", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 151, "name": "credit-moto-151", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Moto", "slug": "credit-moto", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "quand-connait-on-taux-servis-vos-contrats-depargne-assurance-vie"}
