{"questionId": 1879, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment assurer un logement pour un \u00e9tudiant ?", "titleReword": "logement \u00e9tudiant, Prem's, r\u00e9sidence \u00e9tudiante", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 182, "name": "contrat-182", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "contrat-182"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2212, "body": "\"Destin\u00e9 aux \u00e9tudiants, saisonniers et apprentis, le contrat d'assurance logement \u00e9tudiant Prem\u2019s convient aux locataires d'un logement 1 ou 2 pi\u00e8ces. L\u2019ensemble de  leurs biens et ceux de leur \u00e9ventuel colocataire sont couverts sans suppl\u00e9ment, jusqu'\u00e0 hauteur de 7 000 euros. Vous avez plus d\u20191 colocataire ? Un logement de 3 pi\u00e8ces ou plus ? D\u00e9couvrez notre assurance Habitation R\u00e9sidence Principale avec l\u2019option responsabilit\u00e9 locative des colocataires qui est gratuite quel que soit le nombre de vos colocataires.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 182, "name": "contrat-182", "title": "Mon contrat", "slug": "contrat-182", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-assurer-logement-un-etudiant"}
