>Si votre dossier est accept\u00e9 sans n\u00e9cessiter de formalit\u00e9s m\u00e9dicales suppl\u00e9mentaires, vous n\u2019avez plus qu\u2019\u00e0 signer votre contrat en ligne. Ca y est, vous \u00eates assur\u00e9 !\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 150, "name": "credit-auto-150", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Auto", "slug": "credit-auto", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 151, "name": "credit-moto-151", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Moto", "slug": "credit-moto", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 152, "name": "credit-camping-car-152", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Camping-car", "slug": "credit-camping-car", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 153, "name": "credit-bateau-153", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Bateau", "slug": "credit-bateau", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 154, "name": "credit-mobil-home-154", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Mobil-home", "slug": "credit-mobil-home", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 155, "name": "credit-projet-155", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Projet", "slug": "credit-projet", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 156, "name": "credit-travaux-156", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Travaux", "slug": "credit-travaux", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 157, "name": "credit-jeune-157", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Jeune", "slug": "credit-jeune", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 158, "name": "credit-developpement-durable-158", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit D\u00e9veloppement Durable", "slug": "credit-developpement-durable", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-souscrire-contrat-garantie-emprunteur-macif"}
