{"questionId": 1890, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment calculer mon bonus/malus ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 171, "name": "questions-generales-lauto-171", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "questions-generales-lauto"}, {"filterId": 172, "name": "bonus-malus-172", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "bonus-malus"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2223, "body": "\"Egalement appel\u00e9 \\\"coefficient de r\u00e9duction\\/majoration\\\", le coefficient de bonus-malus figure sur l'avis d'\u00e9ch\u00e9ance relatif \u00e0 votre contrat d'assurance auto ou moto.  Si votre coefficient est inf\u00e9rieur \u00e0 1, cela signifie que vous poss\u00e9dez un bonus. S'il est sup\u00e9rieur \u00e0 1, cela signifie que vous possedez un malus. Apr\u00e8s chaque p\u00e9riode annuelle sans sinistre responsable le coefficient est r\u00e9duit de 5% par rapport \u00e0 celui utilis\u00e9 \u00e0 la pr\u00e9c\u00e9dente \u00e9ch\u00e9ance. En cas de sinistre responsable, le coefficient est major\u00e9 de 25%.<br\\/>Calcul du bonus :\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 171, "name": "questions-generales-lauto-171", "title": "Questions g\u00e9n\u00e9rales sur l'Auto", "slug": "questions-generales-lauto", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 172, "name": "bonus-malus-172", "title": "Bonus/malus", "slug": "bonus-malus", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-calculer-bonus-malus-1890"}
