{"questionId": 1915, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment consulter mes devis d'assurance ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 166, "name": "remboursements-166", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "remboursements"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2248, "body": "\"Retrouvez l'ensemble de vos devis m\u00e9moris\u00e9s (assurance auto, habitation, deux-roues, sant\u00e9...) dans votre Espace Assurance, \u00e0 la rubrique \\\"Mes devis\\\".  Une fois connect\u00e9, vous pouvez : obtenir le d\u00e9tail du devis qui vous int\u00e9resse, modifier ses garanties et options, le supprimer de votre liste, le concr\u00e9tiser \u00e0 la date \u00e0 laquelle vous d\u00e9sirez souscrire le contrat.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 166, "name": "remboursements-166", "title": "Mes remboursements", "slug": "remboursements", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-consulter-devis-assurance-1915"}
