{"questionId": 2493, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Quelle est la validit\u00e9 de la carte pr\u00e9pay\u00e9e 12-17 ans ?", "titleReword": "dur\u00e9e carte, dur\u00e9e cb", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 147, "name": "carte-prepayee-12-17-147", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "carte-prepayee-12-17"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2826, "body": "\"La dur\u00e9e de validit\u00e9 de la carte pr\u00e9pay\u00e9e est de 3 ans. La date d\u2019expiration est indiqu\u00e9e sur le recto de la carte de votre enfant.  A l\u2019expiration de la carte, si votre enfant \u00e0 moins de 18 ans, et que vous souhaitez conserver une carte pr\u00e9pay\u00e9e pour lui, il conviendra de faire une nouvelle demande de souscription. L\u2019argent sera automatiquement transf\u00e9r\u00e9 sur la nouvelle carte pr\u00e9pay\u00e9e.  En cas de non renouvellement de la carte, les fonds pr\u00e9sents sur la carte vous seront rembours\u00e9s.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 147, "name": "carte-prepayee-12-17-147", "title": "Carte pr\u00e9pay\u00e9e 12/17", "slug": "carte-prepayee-12-17", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "est-validite-de-carte-prepayee-12-17-ans"}
