{"questionId": 2179, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "En faisant ma demande de cr\u00e9dit par internet, dois-je imprimer l'offre pour la signer et l'envoyer \u00e0 la Macif ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 150, "name": "credit-auto-150", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-auto"}, {"filterId": 151, "name": "credit-moto-151", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-moto"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2512, "body": "\"En r\u00e9alisant votre demande de cr\u00e9dit par internet, il est important que vous t\u00e9l\u00e9chargiez l'offre de cr\u00e9dit pour la conserver. Afin d'accepter cette offre, vous serez invit\u00e9 \u00e0 la signer \u00e9lectroniquement.  Si vous empruntez \u00e0 2, votre co-emprunteur devra \u00e9galement signer \u00e9lectroniquement l'offre de cr\u00e9dit pour l'accepter.  Il n'est pas n\u00e9cessaire de retourner \u00e0 la Macif la version imprim\u00e9e de l'offre.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 150, "name": "credit-auto-150", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Auto", "slug": "credit-auto", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 151, "name": "credit-moto-151", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Moto", "slug": "credit-moto", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "faisant-demande-credit-internet-dois-je-imprimer-offre-la-signer-lenvoyer-la-macif"}
