{"questionId": 2483, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Quelle est la diff\u00e9rence entre un PEP et un LEP ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 158, "name": "credit-developpement-durable-158", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-developpement-durable"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2816, "body": "\"Jusqu\u2019en 2003, le Plan d'\u00c9pargne Populaire PEP \u00e9tait un produit d'\u00e9pargne r\u00e9glement\u00e9 et fiscalement avantageux, tout comme le LEP. Depuis cette date, il n\u2019est plus possible d\u2019en souscrire un, mais les personnes qui d\u00e9tiennent encore un Plan d'\u00c9pargne Populaire peuvent encore le conserver et l'alimenter jusqu'\u00e0 atteindre son plafond.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 158, "name": "credit-developpement-durable-158", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit D\u00e9veloppement Durable", "slug": "credit-developpement-durable", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "est-difference-entre-pep-un-lep"}
