{"questionId": 2170, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment v\u00e9rifier que la t\u00e9l\u00e9transmission fonctionne sur mon contrat ?", "titleReword": "no\u00e9mie, noemie", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 146, "name": "banque-quotidien-146", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "banque-quotidien"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2503, "body": "\"La t\u00e9l\u00e9transmission fonctionne si la mention \\\"Une copie de ce d\u00e9compte est transmise \u00e0 votre organisme compl\u00e9mentaire\\\" figure sur votre d\u00e9compte de S\u00e9curit\u00e9 sociale. Le cas \u00e9ch\u00e9ant, vous devez nous adresser l\u2019original de votre d\u00e9compte:<br\\/>\u2022par mail \u00e0 mutuelle@macif.fr,<br\\/>\u2022ou par courrier \u00e0 Macif-Mutualit\u00e9 79017 NIORT CEDEX.<br\\/> Nous vous invitons \u00e9galement \u00e0 nous contacter au au num\u00e9ro de t\u00e9l\u00e9phone indiqu\u00e9 sur votre carte de tiers payant afin de v\u00e9rifier l\u2019exactitude des \u00e9l\u00e9ments n\u00e9cessaires \u00e0 la mise en place de la t\u00e9l\u00e9transmission.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 146, "name": "banque-quotidien-146", "title": "Banque au quotidien", "slug": "banque-quotidien", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-verifier-la-teletransmission-fonctionne-mon-contrat"}
