{"questionId": 2183, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Est-ce qu\u2019il est possible de modifier les mensualit\u00e9s de mon cr\u00e9dit travaux ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 156, "name": "credit-travaux-156", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-travaux"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2516, "body": "\"Une d\u00e9pense impr\u00e9vue qui survient ?   Vous pouvez faire la demande d'une suspension temporaire de vos mensualit\u00e9s ou d'un r\u00e9am\u00e9nagement de votre cr\u00e9dit travaux pour votre habitat.  Ces modifications se font sans frais ni p\u00e9nalit\u00e9s. Les mensualit\u00e9s de votre emprunt travaux peuvent \u00eatre diff\u00e9r\u00e9es jusqu\u2019\u00e0 3 mois.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 156, "name": "credit-travaux-156", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Travaux", "slug": "credit-travaux", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "est-ce-quil-possible-modifier-mensualites-mon-credit-travaux"}
