{"questionId": 2224, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "J'ai un hoverboard, un gyropode ou gyrogoue, faut-il souscrire une assurance sp\u00e9cifique?", "titleReword": "gyro, hover", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 202, "name": "bon-achat-202", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "bon-achat"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2557, "body": "\"Oui. Les hoverboards, comme les skateboards \u00e9lectriques et autres trottinettes \u00e9lectriques, sont des v\u00e9hicules terrestres \u00e0 moteur au sens du Code des assurances.<br\\/>Il s'agit d'engins de d\u00e9placement personnel motoris\u00e9s ( EDPM ) ou nouveau v\u00e9hicule \u00e9lectrique individuel ( NVEI ) ?<br\\/>Ils sont donc soumis \u00e0 l\u2019obligation d\u2019assurance en Responsabilit\u00e9 Civile automobile.<br\\/>Obligatoire, l\u2019assurance Responsabilit\u00e9 civile couvre le conducteur pour les dommages corporels et mat\u00e9riels qu\u2019il peut causer aux autres avec son engin.  \u00c0 la Macif, nous avons des solutions d'assurance hoverboard, assurance gyropode ou assurance gyroroue qui peuvent r\u00e9pondre \u00e0 cette obligation d'assurance.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 202, "name": "bon-achat-202", "title": "Bon d'achat", "slug": "bon-achat", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "title": "Macif Avantages", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "ai-hoverboard-un-gyropode-gyrogoue-faut-il-souscrire-assurance-specifique"}
