{"questionId": 2156, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment supprimer mon espace personnel ?", "titleReword": "supprimer espace, espace personnel, suppression espace, espace client, espace soci\u00e9taire", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 165, "name": "contrat-165", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "contrat"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2489, "body": "\"Vous avez le choix entre deux possibilit\u00e9s :<br\\/>\u2022vous souhaitez modifier vos pr\u00e9f\u00e9rences de contact, nous vous invitons \u00e0 vous rendre sur votre espace personnel,<br\\/>\u2022pour toute autre demande, rendez-vous sur la rubrique \\\"Contacts\\\" de notre page consacr\u00e9e \u00e0 la gestion de vos donn\u00e9es personnelles.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 165, "name": "contrat-165", "title": "Mon contrat", "slug": "contrat", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-supprimer-espace-personnel"}
