{"questionId": 2464, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Quel est le tarif de l'assurance association ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 169, "name": "rac-0-169", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "rac-0"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2797, "body": "\"Le tarif de l\u2019assurance association est fonction de vos activit\u00e9s, de votre budget ou encore du nombre d\u2019adh\u00e9rents de votre association. Notre contrat d\u2019assurance association s\u2019adapte \u00e9galement \u00e0 vos besoins : Locaux de l\u2019association, Biens dont vous disposez (mat\u00e9riel, mobilier, informatique), Des garanties souhait\u00e9es en cas d\u2019accident corporel. N\u2019h\u00e9sitez pas \u00e0 demander votre \u00e9tude personnalis\u00e9e : En ligne, Par t\u00e9l\u00e9phone au 09 69 39 49 55 ( Appel non surtax\u00e9 ), du lundi au vendredi de 8h30 \u00e0 18h30.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 169, "name": "rac-0-169", "title": "Rac 0", "slug": "rac-0", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "est-tarif-assurance-association"}
