{"questionId": 2211, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "J'ai entendu dire que je devais conserver l'assurance bancaire au moins un an, est-ce vrai ?", "titleReword": "assurance bancaire,d\u00e9l\u00e9gation d'assurance, changement assurance de pr\u00eat", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 211, "name": "adidas-211", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "adidas"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2544, "body": "\"Non. Vous avez la possibilit\u00e9 de changer d\u2019assurance de pr\u00eat \u00e0 n\u2019importe quel moment dans l\u2019ann\u00e9e qui suit la signature de l\u2019offre de pr\u00eat immobilier, et ce m\u00eame d\u00e8s le lendemain de cette signature (en respectant un d\u00e9lai de pr\u00e9avis de 15 jours) !  Si vous ne souhaitez pas n\u00e9gocier une d\u00e9l\u00e9gation d\u2019assurance au moment de votre n\u00e9gociation avec votre banquier sur votre cr\u00e9dit, montez votre dossier Garantie Emprunteur de la Macif en parall\u00e8le afin de pouvoir faire la substitution rapidement.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 211, "name": "adidas-211", "title": "Adidas", "slug": "adidas", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "title": "Macif Avantages", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "ai-entendu-dire-je-devais-conserver-assurance-bancaire-moins-an-est-ce-vrai"}
