{"questionId": 2126, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment r\u00e9silier une assurance sant\u00e9 apr\u00e8s hausse de tarif ?", "titleReword": "r\u00e9siliation, r\u00e9silier, contrat, assurance sant\u00e9", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 278, "name": "billetterie-278", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "billetterie"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2459, "body": "\"Pour r\u00e9silier un contrat d\u2019assurance sant\u00e9 apr\u00e8s une augmentation de la cotisation, vous disposez d\u2019un d\u00e9lai de 30 jours \u00e0 partir de la date de r\u00e9ception de votre nouvel avis d\u2019\u00e9ch\u00e9ance.  Votre demande de r\u00e9siliation doit nous \u00eatre envoy\u00e9e en lettre recommand\u00e9e papier ou un recommand\u00e9 \u00e9lectronique avec demande d'avis de r\u00e9ception \u00e0 l\u2019adresse suivante : Macif-Mutualit\u00e9 79017 Niort Cedex ou \u00e0 mutuelle@macif.fr .\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 278, "name": "billetterie-278", "title": "La billetterie", "slug": "billetterie", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "title": "Macif Avantages", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "comment-resilier-assurance-sante-apres-hausse-tarif"}
