{"questionId": 2337, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Peut-on mettre en place un rechargement programm\u00e9 ?", "titleReword": "recharger", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 147, "name": "carte-prepayee-12-17-147", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "carte-prepayee-12-17"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2670, "body": "\"Oui, il est possible de programmer le rechargement de la carte pr\u00e9pay\u00e9e. Il est \u00e9galement possible de choisir : le montant, la fr\u00e9quence, la devise, la date de d\u00e9but du rechargement programm\u00e9, directement depuis votre espace de gestion.  Il vous suffit de cliquer sur l\u2019onglet \u00abOp\u00e9rations\u00bb, puis sur le bouton \u00abAjouter une op\u00e9ration automatique\u00bb.  En cas de d\u00e9tention de plusieurs cartes, vous pouvez choisir la carte sur laquelle vous souhaitez mettre en place le rechargement programm\u00e9.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 147, "name": "carte-prepayee-12-17-147", "title": "Carte pr\u00e9pay\u00e9e 12/17", "slug": "carte-prepayee-12-17", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "peut-on-mettre-place-rechargement-programme"}
