{"questionId": 2283, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Les frais d'ost\u00e9opathe peuvent-ils \u00eatre rembours\u00e9s ?", "titleReword": "osteo, ost\u00e9o, osth\u00e9o, ostheo", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 162, "name": "questions-generales-162", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "questions-generales-162"}, {"filterId": 164, "name": "garanties-164", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "garanties"}, {"filterId": 166, "name": "remboursements-166", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "remboursements"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2616, "body": "\"Les frais d'ost\u00e9opathe sont pris en charge par votre contrat de compl\u00e9mentaire sant\u00e9, dans la limite de 3 s\u00e9ances par ann\u00e9e civile, en formule :  Equilibr\u00e9e : \u00e0 hauteur de 35 \u20ac par s\u00e9ance, Protectrice : \u00e0 hauteur de 40 \u20ac par s\u00e9ance, Excellence : \u00e0 hauteur de 45 \u20ac par s\u00e9ance.<br\\/> Pour obtenir le remboursement, vous devez nous adresser la facture aquitt\u00e9e et d\u00e9taill\u00e9e :<br\\/> par mail \u00e0 mutuelle@macif.fr, ou par courrier \u00e0 Macif-Mutualit\u00e9 79017 Niort Cedex.<br\\/> Le d\u00e9lai de remboursement est de 2 jours ouvr\u00e9s \u00e0 compter de la r\u00e9ception des justificatifs.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 162, "name": "questions-generales-162", "title": "Questions g\u00e9n\u00e9rales", "slug": "questions-generales-162", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 164, "name": "garanties-164", "title": "Mes garanties", "slug": "garanties", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 166, "name": "remboursements-166", "title": "Mes remboursements", "slug": "remboursements", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "frais-osteopathe-peuvent-ils-etre-rembourses"}
