{"questionId": 2223, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "J'ai un contrat Macif Pann'Auto : Comment d\u00e9clarer mon sinistre ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 164, "name": "garanties-164", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "garanties"}, {"filterId": 182, "name": "contrat-182", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "contrat-182"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2556, "body": "\"En cas de panne survenue en France m\u00e9tropolitaine ou \u00e0 l'\u00e9tranger, et susceptible de mettre en \u0153uvre la garantie du contrat, vous devez la d\u00e9clarer d\u00e8s que vous en avez connaissance et au plus tard dans les cinq jours ouvr\u00e9s, sur votre espace internet Macif Pann\u2019Auto ou \u00e0 l\u2019adresse Macif Pann\u2019Auto 31 route de Gachet 44300 Nantes.  Pour savoir Comment b\u00e9n\u00e9ficier de la prise en charge avec Macif Pann'Auto en cas de panne de votre v\u00e9hicule, cliquez ici\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 164, "name": "garanties-164", "title": "Mes garanties", "slug": "garanties", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 182, "name": "contrat-182", "title": "Mon contrat", "slug": "contrat-182", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "ai-contrat-macif-pannauto-comment-declarer-sinistre"}
