{"questionId": 2510, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Quelles sont les d\u00e9marches pour organiser un \u00e9v\u00e8nement, une animation, sur la voie publique ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 221, "name": "cdiscount-221", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "cdiscount"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2843, "body": "\"Si vous souhaitez organiser un \u00e9v\u00e8nement sur la voie publique, vous devez respecter plusieurs obligations dont celles de d\u00e9claration pr\u00e9alable de la manifestation\\/rassembement.<br\\/>Nous vous invitons \u00e0 v\u00e9rifier vos obligations sur le site www.service-public.fr.<br\\/> Le contrat Multigarantie Activit\u00e9s Sociales Vie associative Macif pr\u00e9voit la garantie responsabilit\u00e9 civile \u00e0 l\u2019occasion de l\u2019organisation d\u2019un \u00e9v\u00e8nement (festivit\u00e9, repas annuel, rencontre), y compris si vous souhaitez louer une salle pour l\u2019organiser.<br\\/> Pour ce type de d\u00e9marche merci de contacter nos services.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 221, "name": "cdiscount-221", "title": "Cdiscount", "slug": "cdiscount", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "title": "Macif Avantages", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "sont-demarches-organiser-un-evenement-une-animation-sur-voie-publique"}
