{"questionId": 2557, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Quels types de travaux puis-je financer avec le cr\u00e9dit d\u00e9veloppement durable Macif ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 167, "name": "garantie-sante-madelin-167", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "garantie-sante-madelin"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2890, "body": "\"Ce cr\u00e9dit, r\u00e9serv\u00e9 aux propri\u00e9taires, permet le financement de biens d\u2019\u00e9quipement performants au plan \u00e9nerg\u00e9tique ou utilisant des \u00e9nergies renouvelables \u00e9ligibles \u00e0 un cr\u00e9dit d'imp\u00f4ts : r\u00e9novations lourdes d\u2019isolation thermique de l\u2019habitat, chaudi\u00e8res \u00e0 condensation et \u00e9quipements de production d\u2019\u00e9nergie utilisant une source d\u2019\u00e9nergie renouvelable.  Les travaux doivent \u00eatre r\u00e9alis\u00e9s par un artisan agr\u00e9\u00e9 RGE  Plus d'informations sur le cr\u00e9dit d'imp\u00f4ts sur le site du service public\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 167, "name": "garantie-sante-madelin-167", "title": "Garantie sant\u00e9 madelin", "slug": "garantie-sante-madelin", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "types-travaux-puis-je-financer-le-credit-developpement-durable-macif"}
