{"questionId": 2538, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Quels sont les justificatifs \u00e0 fournir pour obtenir mon cr\u00e9dit camping-car ou caravane ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 155, "name": "credit-projet-155", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-projet"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2871, "body": "\"Pour compl\u00e9ter votre dossier de cr\u00e9dit, il vous faudra fournir: un justificatif d'achat du bien \u00e0 financer,  un certificat de non gage si le bien \u00e0 financer est un v\u00e9hicule d'occasion,  un RIB pour vos remboursements et, pour chaque emprunteur, un justificatif d'identit\u00e9 et un justificatif de domicile et de revenus de moins de 3 mois.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 155, "name": "credit-projet-155", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Projet", "slug": "credit-projet", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "sont-justificatifs-fournir-obtenir-credit-camping-car-caravane"}
