{"questionId": 2256, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Je suis tomb\u00e9 en panne. Que faire ?", "titleReword": "d\u00e9pannage, d\u00e9panneur, remorquage", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 323, "name": "boulanger-pro-323", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "boulanger-pro"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2589, "body": "\"En tant que soci\u00e9taire Macif, si votre voiture est en panne, vous devez contacter Macif Assistance. Disponible 24\\/24h et 7\\/7j, ce service est joignable au num\u00e9ro de t\u00e9l\u00e9phone indiqu\u00e9 au dos de votre carte verte. Un conseiller fera le point avec vous sur votre situation (nature de la panne, lieu de la panne...) et mettra en oeuvre les garanties d'assistance dans les conditions pr\u00e9vues par votre contrat, le cas \u00e9ch\u00e9ant.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 323, "name": "boulanger-pro-323", "title": "Boulanger pro", "slug": "boulanger-pro", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "title": "Macif Avantages", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "suis-tombe-en-panne-que-faire"}
