{"questionId": 2302, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Mon assurance obs\u00e8ques Macif pr\u00e9voit-il une clause de revalorisation des garanties ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 192, "name": "garantie-obseques-192", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "garantie-obseques"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2635, "body": "\"Oui, votre assurance obs\u00e8ques Macif pr\u00e9voit une revalorisation des garanties. La revalorisation est le m\u00e9canisme qui permet de faire \u00e9voluer, \u00e0 chaque \u00e9ch\u00e9ance du contrat, les montants de garanties en fonction de l'\u00e9volution du co\u00fbt de la vie. Elle est vis\u00e9e dans la notice d'information de votre contrat.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 192, "name": "garantie-obseques-192", "title": "Garantie obs\u00e8ques", "slug": "garantie-obseques", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "assurance-obseques-macif-prevoit-il-clause-revalorisation-garanties"}
