{"questionId": 2308, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Mon produit re\u00e7u ne me satisfait pas : comment utiliser mon droit de r\u00e9tractation ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 276, "name": "marketplace-276", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "marketplace"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2641, "body": "\"Vous disposez d'un d\u00e9lai de 14 jours \u00e0 compter de la date de r\u00e9ception du produit pour exercer votre droit de r\u00e9tractation sans avoir \u00e0 justifier de motifs ni \u00e0 payer de p\u00e9nalit\u00e9s. Pour cela, connectez vous sur La MarketPlace Macif Avantages gr\u00e2ce \u00e0 votre Email et votre mot de passe. Ensuite, vous allez sur \\\"MON COMPTE\\\" puis sur \\\"Mes commandes\\\" puis \\\"Contacter le Marchand\\\".\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 276, "name": "marketplace-276", "title": "La marketplace", "slug": "marketplace", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "title": "Macif Avantages", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "produit-recu-me-satisfait-pas-comment-utiliser-droit-retractation"}
