{"questionId": 2257, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Je suis un particulier, puis-je effectuer une commande aupr\u00e8s de Boulanger Pro ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 165, "name": "contrat-165", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "contrat"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2590, "body": "\"Notre partenariat avec Boulanger Pro est accessible \u00e0 l'ensemble des soci\u00e9taires Macif, y compris aux particuliers. Vous pouvez consulter les offres de Boulanger Pro en vous connectant sur le site www.macifavantages.fr puis en cliquant sur Boulanger Pro. Sur la page de pr\u00e9sentation de notre partenariat, cliquez sur le lien \\\"J'en profite\\\" puis sur \\\"Je Commande\\\".\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 165, "name": "contrat-165", "title": "Mon contrat", "slug": "contrat", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "suis-particulier-puis-je-effectuer-commande-aupres-boulanger-pro"}
