{"questionId": 2400, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Puis-je suspendre temporairement mes remboursements ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 56, "name": "professionnels-56", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 150, "name": "credit-auto-150", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-auto"}, {"filterId": 151, "name": "credit-moto-151", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-moto"}, {"filterId": 152, "name": "credit-camping-car-152", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-camping-car"}, {"filterId": 153, "name": "credit-bateau-153", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-bateau"}, {"filterId": 154, "name": "credit-mobil-home-154", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-mobil-home"}, {"filterId": 155, "name": "credit-projet-155", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-projet"}, {"filterId": 156, "name": "credit-travaux-156", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-travaux"}, {"filterId": 157, "name": "credit-jeune-157", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-jeune"}, {"filterId": 158, "name": "credit-developpement-durable-158", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-developpement-durable"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2733, "body": "\"Vous pouvez reporter des \u00e9ch\u00e9ances en fin de cr\u00e9dit dans la limite maximale de 3 \u00e9ch\u00e9ances pour toute la dur\u00e9e de votre pr\u00eat selon le type de cr\u00e9dit souscrit.  Contactez votre conseiller Macifin' pour lui pr\u00e9ciser votre demande. Apr\u00e8s \u00e9tude et accord de Socram Banque, un avenant vous sera adress\u00e9. D\u00e8s r\u00e9ception de l'avenant sign\u00e9, les nouvelles conditions de remboursement rentreront en vigueur.  A savoir : l'\u00e9ch\u00e9ance de reprise est major\u00e9e du montant des int\u00e9r\u00eats et des cotisations courus pendant le report des mensualit\u00e9s.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 150, "name": "credit-auto-150", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Auto", "slug": "credit-auto", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 151, "name": "credit-moto-151", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Moto", "slug": "credit-moto", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 152, "name": "credit-camping-car-152", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Camping-car", "slug": "credit-camping-car", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 153, "name": "credit-bateau-153", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Bateau", "slug": "credit-bateau", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 154, "name": "credit-mobil-home-154", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Mobil-home", "slug": "credit-mobil-home", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 155, "name": "credit-projet-155", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Projet", "slug": "credit-projet", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 156, "name": "credit-travaux-156", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Travaux", "slug": "credit-travaux", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 157, "name": "credit-jeune-157", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Jeune", "slug": "credit-jeune", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 158, "name": "credit-developpement-durable-158", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit D\u00e9veloppement Durable", "slug": "credit-developpement-durable", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 56, "name": "professionnels-56", "title": "Professionnels", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "puis-je-suspendre-temporairement-remboursements-2400"}
