{"questionId": 2589, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Qu'est-ce que le fonds mutuel de garantie ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 150, "name": "credit-auto-150", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-auto"}, {"filterId": 151, "name": "credit-moto-151", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-moto"}, {"filterId": 152, "name": "credit-camping-car-152", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-camping-car"}, {"filterId": 153, "name": "credit-bateau-153", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-bateau"}, {"filterId": 154, "name": "credit-mobil-home-154", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-mobil-home"}, {"filterId": 155, "name": "credit-projet-155", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-projet"}, {"filterId": 156, "name": "credit-travaux-156", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-travaux"}, {"filterId": 157, "name": "credit-jeune-157", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-jeune"}, {"filterId": 158, "name": "credit-developpement-durable-158", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-developpement-durable"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2922, "body": "\"Le Fonds Mutuel de garantie de votre cr\u00e9dit conso est un dispositif r\u00e9serv\u00e9 aux soci\u00e9taires Macif.<br\\/>Il peut se substituer de mani\u00e8re temporaire aux emprunteurs connaissant des difficult\u00e9s financi\u00e8res et ne pouvant plus assumer le remboursement de leurs mensualit\u00e9s. Il est bas\u00e9 sur la mutualisation des risques : chaque emprunteur verse 2% de la somme emprunt\u00e9e.<br\\/>L'\u00e9tablissement financier se porte ainsi garant du cr\u00e9dit r\u00e9alis\u00e9. Son montant vous est rembours\u00e9 un mois apr\u00e8s le remboursement total de votre cr\u00e9dit.<br\\/>Par exemple, sur 15 000 \u20ac emprunt\u00e9s, vous serez rembours\u00e9 de 300 \u20ac.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 150, "name": "credit-auto-150", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Auto", "slug": "credit-auto", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 151, "name": "credit-moto-151", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Moto", "slug": "credit-moto", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 152, "name": "credit-camping-car-152", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Camping-car", "slug": "credit-camping-car", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 153, "name": "credit-bateau-153", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Bateau", "slug": "credit-bateau", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 154, "name": "credit-mobil-home-154", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Mobil-home", "slug": "credit-mobil-home", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 155, "name": "credit-projet-155", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Projet", "slug": "credit-projet", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 156, "name": "credit-travaux-156", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Travaux", "slug": "credit-travaux", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 157, "name": "credit-jeune-157", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Jeune", "slug": "credit-jeune", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 158, "name": "credit-developpement-durable-158", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit D\u00e9veloppement Durable", "slug": "credit-developpement-durable", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "est-ce-le-fonds-mutuel-garantie"}
