{"questionId": 2230, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Je change l'immatriculation de mon v\u00e9hicule; que dois-je faire ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 182, "name": "contrat-182", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "contrat-182"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2563, "body": "\"Pour modifier votre immatriculation, nous vous invitons \u00e0 utiliser au choix plusieurs solutions: \u2022Nous contacter par t\u00e9l\u00e9phone (rubrique \\\"Appeler un conseiller\\\", puis \\\"Assurance (auto, habitation, etc.)\\\",  \u2022Vous rendre dans votre agence macif la plus proche,  \u2022Nous \u00e9crire gr\u00e2ce au formulaire de contact dans votre Espace Assurance.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 182, "name": "contrat-182", "title": "Mon contrat", "slug": "contrat-182", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "change-immatriculation-mon-vehicule-que-dois-je-faire-2230"}
