{"questionId": 2601, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Qui est assur\u00e9 lors d\u2019une activit\u00e9 organis\u00e9e par l'association ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 62, "name": "associations-cse-62", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 309, "name": "activites-309", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "activites-309"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2934, "body": "\"Les adh\u00e9rents, b\u00e9n\u00e9voles, salari\u00e9s et volontaires service civique de l'association sont assur\u00e9s au titre de la garantie du contrat Multigarantie Activit\u00e9s Sociales Vie associative souscrit par l'association.<br\\/> Si vous \u00eates une association sportive la garantie responsabilit\u00e9 civile est \u00e9tendue \u00e0 toutes personnes que vous invitez \u00e0 participer ponctuellement \u00e0 vos activit\u00e9s sportives, ou celles accueillies temporairement \u00e0 titre d\u2019essai dans le cadre de ces activit\u00e9s\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 309, "name": "activites-309", "title": "Activit\u00e9s", "slug": "activites-309", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 62, "name": "associations-cse-62", "title": "Associations - CSE", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "assure-lors-dune-activite-organisee-lassociation"}
