{"questionId": 2359, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Proposez-vous l'assurance voiture de collection ?", "titleReword": "voiture de collection, collection, v\u00e9hicule de collection", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 171, "name": "questions-generales-lauto-171", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "questions-generales-lauto"}, {"filterId": 174, "name": "contrat-174", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "contrat-174"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2692, "body": "\"A la Macif, vous pouvez prendre votre assurance voiture de collection (v\u00e9hicule particulier) \u00e0 des conditions tarifaires avantageuses. Pour en b\u00e9n\u00e9ficier, vous devez utiliser ce v\u00e9hicule pour un usage priv\u00e9 uniquement et bien entendu la mention \\\"v\u00e9hicule de collection\\\" doit \u00eatre appos\u00e9e sur votre carte grise en ligne Z1. Pour obtenir un tarif et le d\u00e9tail des garanties propos\u00e9es, il vous suffit simplement de nous contacter par t\u00e9l\u00e9phone ou de vous d\u00e9placer dans l'une de nos agences.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 171, "name": "questions-generales-lauto-171", "title": "Questions g\u00e9n\u00e9rales sur l'Auto", "slug": "questions-generales-lauto", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 174, "name": "contrat-174", "title": "Mon contrat", "slug": "contrat-174", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "proposez-vous-assurance-voiture-collection"}
