{"questionId": 2398, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Puis-je souscrire une assurance voyage ?", "titleReword": "assurer un voyage", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 164, "name": "garanties-164", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "garanties"}, {"filterId": 182, "name": "contrat-182", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "contrat-182"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2731, "body": "\"La Macif ne propose pas d'assurance voyage en cas d'annulation ou de perte de bagage par exemple.<br\\/>En revanche, plusieurs contrats (auto, garantie accident par exemple) pr\u00e9voient une assistance aux personnes en d\u00e9placement en cas d\u2019accident ou de maladie. Macif Assistance intervient 24h\\/24 partout en France et \u00e0 l'\u00e9tranger (rapatriement, avance sur frais m\u00e9dicaux, d'hospitalisation \u00e0 l'\u00e9tranger,...), pour porter secours \u00e0 l\u2019assur\u00e9, son conjoint et ses enfants.<br\\/> Vous partez \u00e0 l'\u00e9tranger ? Retrouvez nos conseils.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 164, "name": "garanties-164", "title": "Mes garanties", "slug": "garanties", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 182, "name": "contrat-182", "title": "Mon contrat", "slug": "contrat-182", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "puis-je-souscrire-assurance-voyage"}
