{"questionId": 2339, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Peut-on se faire rembourser l'assurance CE/CSE/CAS/COS ?", "titleReword": "rc", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 62, "name": "associations-cse-62", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 309, "name": "activites-309", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "activites-309"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2672, "body": "\"Seuls les CE ou CSE, peuvent se faire rembourser la garantie responsabilit\u00e9 civile de leur contrat d\u2019assurance par l\u2019employeur (Art. R.2323-34 du code du travail).<br\\/>Pour ce faire, une attestation d\u2019assurance est \u00e0 votre disposition dans votre espace personnel.<br\\/> Comment ouvrir \u00e0 mon espace personnel Asso ou CSE ? Mode d'emploi.<br\\/>Comment acc\u00e9der \u00e0 mon espace personnel particulier ?\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 309, "name": "activites-309", "title": "Activit\u00e9s", "slug": "activites-309", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 62, "name": "associations-cse-62", "title": "Associations - CSE", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "peut-on-faire-rembourser-assurance-ce-cse-cas-cos"}
