{"questionId": 2460, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Quel est le montant maximum par achat avec la carte pr\u00e9pay\u00e9e ?", "titleReword": "paiement maxi, paiement maximum, plafond paiement", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 62, "name": "associations-cse-62", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 305, "name": "activites-305", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "activites"}, {"filterId": 306, "name": "biens-locaux-306", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "biens-locaux"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2793, "body": "\"Votre enfant ne pourra pas d\u00e9penser au-del\u00e0 des sommes disponibles sur sa carte pr\u00e9pay\u00e9e, les d\u00e9couverts n\u2019\u00e9tant pas autoris\u00e9s.  N\u00e9anmoins, pensez \u00e0 pr\u00e9voir assez de cr\u00e9dit sur la carte rechargeable pour couvrir \u00e9galement les \u00e9ventuels frais de transaction chez certains commer\u00e7ants.  Les d\u00e9penses s\u2019effectuent dans le respect du plafond de rechargement (300 \u20ac, 600 \u20ac et 1 000 \u20ac) que vous avez autoris\u00e9 \u00e0 votre enfant.  Pour plus de d\u00e9tails : Consultez les Conditions g\u00e9n\u00e9rales en vigueur au 22 Mai 2019.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 305, "name": "activites-305", "title": "Activit\u00e9s", "slug": "activites", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 306, "name": "biens-locaux-306", "title": "Biens et locaux", "slug": "biens-locaux", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 62, "name": "associations-cse-62", "title": "Associations - CSE", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "est-montant-maximum-achat-la-carte-prepayee"}
