{"questionId": 2346, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Pourquoi dois-je voter pour une liste d'union et comment est-elle constitu\u00e9e ?", "titleReword": "liste \u00e9lectorale, liste, \u00e9lections, elire", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 197, "name": "delegues-197", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "delegues"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2679, "body": "\"Les listes d\u2019union sont compos\u00e9es par des candidats repr\u00e9sentatifs de la diversit\u00e9 du soci\u00e9tariat (professionnels ind\u00e9pendants, employeurs, grandes conf\u00e9d\u00e9rations syndicales de salari\u00e9s, mouvements coop\u00e9ratifs, associatifs et mutualistes, individuels). Ainsi, les assur\u00e9s sont repr\u00e9sent\u00e9s par des d\u00e9l\u00e9gu\u00e9s proches de leur quotidien et de leurs pr\u00e9occupations.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 197, "name": "delegues-197", "title": "Les d\u00e9l\u00e9gu\u00e9s", "slug": "delegues", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "pourquoi-dois-je-voter-une-liste-union-comment-constituee"}
