{"questionId": 2350, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Pourquoi je n'arrive pas \u00e0 faire de devis ?", "titleReword": "erreur devis en ligne, \u00e9tude personnalis\u00e9e auto, devis auto impossible, devis auto probl\u00e8mes, contacter probl\u00e8me devis auto", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 174, "name": "contrat-174", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "contrat-174"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2683, "body": "\"Dans certaines situations particuli\u00e8res (conducteur et\\/ou v\u00e9hicule), nous ne pouvons proposer de devis d'assurance auto en ligne personnalis\u00e9. Dans ce cas, nous vous invitons \u00e0 en faire la demande en utilisant le mode de contact qui vous convient :<br\\/> nous \u00e9crire gr\u00e2ce au formulaire de contact, ou contacter votre conseiller par t\u00e9l\u00e9phone, ou vous d\u00e9placer dans un point d'accueil Macif le plus proche de chez vous.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 174, "name": "contrat-174", "title": "Mon contrat", "slug": "contrat-174", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "pourquoi-narrive-faire-devis"}
