{"questionId": 2622, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Si je poss\u00e8de plusieurs v\u00e9hicules, avoir un accident avec un v\u00e9hicule aura-t-il une incidence sur le taux de bonus malus affect\u00e9 aux autres v\u00e9hicules ?", "titleReword": "couverture accident v\u00e9hicules, assurance auto couverture, incidence bonus malus vehicule, incidence taux bonus malus, plusieurs vehicules accident", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 172, "name": "bonus-malus-172", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "bonus-malus"}, {"filterId": 177, "name": "sinistres-177", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "sinistres"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2955, "body": "\"Le contrat d'assurance Auto Macif ne couvre qu'un seul v\u00e9hicule (plusieurs v\u00e9hicules = plusieurs contrats). En cons\u00e9quence, un sinistre responsable n'augmentera que le coefficient bonus malus du v\u00e9hicule impliqu\u00e9, et non celui des autres v\u00e9hicules que vous poss\u00e9dez.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 172, "name": "bonus-malus-172", "title": "Bonus/malus", "slug": "bonus-malus", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 177, "name": "sinistres-177", "title": "Mes sinistres", "slug": "sinistres", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "si-possede-plusieurs-vehicules-avoir-accident-un-vehicule-aura-t-il-incidence-taux-bonus-malus-affecte-aux-autres-vehicules"}
