{"questionId": 2595, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Qu'est-ce qu'un cr\u00e9dit affect\u00e9 ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 150, "name": "credit-auto-150", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-auto"}, {"filterId": 151, "name": "credit-moto-151", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-moto"}, {"filterId": 152, "name": "credit-camping-car-152", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-camping-car"}, {"filterId": 153, "name": "credit-bateau-153", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-bateau"}, {"filterId": 154, "name": "credit-mobil-home-154", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-mobil-home"}, {"filterId": 155, "name": "credit-projet-155", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-projet"}, {"filterId": 156, "name": "credit-travaux-156", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-travaux"}, {"filterId": 158, "name": "credit-developpement-durable-158", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-developpement-durable"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2928, "body": "\"La pr\u00e9sentation de devis ou de factures est n\u00e9cessaire pour r\u00e9aliser ce type de cr\u00e9dit. Le cr\u00e9dit obtenu doit servir uniquement \u00e0 payer le bien d\u00e9fini.<br\\/>Si le contrat de vente ne se r\u00e9alise pas (d\u00e9sistement de votre part...), l'annulation du contrat de cr\u00e9dit sera automatique, m\u00eame si celui-ci vous a d\u00e9j\u00e0 \u00e9t\u00e9 accord\u00e9.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 150, "name": "credit-auto-150", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Auto", "slug": "credit-auto", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 151, "name": "credit-moto-151", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Moto", "slug": "cred