{"questionId": 2420, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Quand serais-je pr\u00e9lev\u00e9 pour la premi\u00e8re fois pour mon pr\u00eat d\u00e9veloppement durable ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 171, "name": "questions-generales-lauto-171", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "questions-generales-lauto"}, {"filterId": 173, "name": "garanties-173", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "garanties-173"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2753, "body": "\"Dans le cadre du remboursement de votre pr\u00eat vert, votre premier pr\u00e9l\u00e8vement intervient 30 jours apr\u00e8s que votre demande de d\u00e9blocage des fonds (1, 5, 10, 15, 20 ou le 25 de chaque mois). Par exemple, si vous d\u00e9bloquez vos fonds le 11\\/06, vous serez ainsi pr\u00e9lev\u00e9 le 15\\/07. Vous pouvez aussi modifier votre date de pr\u00e9l\u00e8vement pour l'adapter \u00e0 celle du versement de votre revenu, moyennant le paiement d\u2019int\u00e9r\u00eats intercalaires.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 171, "name": "questions-generales-lauto-171", "title": "Questions g\u00e9n\u00e9rales sur l'Auto", "slug": "questions-generales-lauto", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 173, "name": "garanties-173", "title": "Mes garanties", "slug": "garanties-173", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "quand-serais-je-preleve-pour-premiere-fois-mon-pret-developpe