{"questionId": 2590, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Qu'est-ce que le mandat de r\u00e9siliation ?", "titleReword": "mandat de r\u00e9siliation", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 184, "name": "assurance-emprunteur-184", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "assurance-emprunteur"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2923, "body": "\"En cas de changement d\u2019assurance en cours de pr\u00eat au b\u00e9n\u00e9fice du contrat Garantie Emprunteur de la Macif, nous prenons en charge gratuitement toutes les formalit\u00e9s aupr\u00e8s de votre banque, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la substitution effective. Afin de pouvoir effectuer ces d\u00e9marches en votre nom, vous devez nous signer un mandat de r\u00e9siliation qui nous y autorise express\u00e9ment. \u00c0 nous les formalit\u00e9s, \u00e0 vous les \u00e9conomies !\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 184, "name": "assurance-emprunteur-184", "title": "Assurance emprunteur", "slug": "assurance-emprunteur", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": -1, "questionSlug": "est-ce-le-mandat-resiliation"}
