{"questionId": 2468, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Quel impact de la r\u00e9forme 100 % Sant\u00e9 sur les prix des soins ?", "titleReword": "reste charge", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 56, "name": "professionnels-56", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 301, "name": "epargne-retraite-301", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "epargne-retraite"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2801, "body": "\"La r\u00e9forme 100 % Sant\u00e9 va impacter le prix de certaines proth\u00e8ses.<br\\/>Ainsi, d\u00e8s 2019, les prix limites de vente pour une proth\u00e8se auditive sont de 1 300 \u20ac pour un adulte et 1 400 \u20ac pour les enfants jusqu\u2019\u00e0 leurs 20 ans. <br\\/>La proth\u00e8se auditive adulte 100% sant\u00e9 verra son prix baisser \u00e0 nouveau en 2020 pour atteindre 1 100 \u20ac.<br\\/>En 2021, le prix de ce m\u00eame \u00e9quipement sera de 950 \u20ac. Avril 2019 a donn\u00e9 le coup d'envoi des premi\u00e8res limitations d'honoraires pour certaines proth\u00e8ses dentaires.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 301, "name": "epargne-retraite-301", "title": "Epargne Retraite", "slug": "epargne-retraite", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 56, "name": "professionnels-56", "title": "Professionnels", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "impact-reforme-100-sante-sur-prix-soins"}
