{"questionId": 2586, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Qu'est-ce que le certificat d'\u00e9quivalence de garanties Macif ?", "titleReword": "\u00e9quivalence de garanties,emprunteur", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 279, "name": "comparateur-voyages-279", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "comparateur-voyages"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2919, "body": "\"Afin de pouvoir souscrire une assurance autre que celle propos\u00e9e par la banque, vous devez pr\u00e9senter un contrat d'un niveau de garanties \u00e9quivalent \u00e0 celle-ci. C\u2019est pourquoi le contrat Garantie Emprunteur de la Macif s\u2019adapte automatiquement et reprend toutes les garanties de votre banque. Pour le prouver, nous vous fournissons, ainsi qu\u2019\u00e0 votre banque, un certificat d\u2019\u00e9quivalence de garanties *.  * Certificat d'\u00e9quivalence de garanties d\u00e9livr\u00e9 sous conditions, sauf r\u00e9serves m\u00e9dicales sp\u00e9cifiques mentionn\u00e9es aux conditions particuli\u00e8res.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 279, "name": "comparateur-voyages-279", "title": "Le comparateur de Voyages", "slug": "comparateur-voyages", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "title": "Macif Avantages", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "est-ce-le-certificat-dequivalence-garanties-macif"}
