{"questionId": 2638, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Suis-je couvert en cas d'accident de ski ?", "titleReword": "accident ski, garantie ski, garantie accident ski, responsabilit\u00e9 civile ski, assurance secours montagne, accident snowboard", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 194, "name": "loisirs-194", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "loisirs"}, {"filterId": 200, "name": "sinistres-200", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "sinistres-200"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2971, "body": "\"Lorsque vous faites du ski, vous \u00eates convert pour les dommages caus\u00e9s \u00e0 un tiers, par la garantie responsabilit\u00e9 civile de votre contrat Habitation R\u00e9sidence principale, dans les conditions et limites indiqu\u00e9es dans les conditions g\u00e9n\u00e9rales.  Pour vos propres dommages, ainsi que pour les frais de recherche et les frais de secours, vous serez couvert si vous avez souscrit le contrat Garantie Accident.  Ce contrat couvre aussi la prise en charge des frais de recherche et de secours en montagne **.  * Voir les conditions du contrat Garantie Accident  ** Dans la limite du plafond d\u00e9fini au contrat.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 194, "name": "loisirs-194", "title": "Mes loisirs", "slug": "loisirs", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 200, "name": "sinistres-200", "title": "Sinistres", "slug": "sinistres-200", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "freque