{"questionId": 2625, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Soci\u00e9taire, adh\u00e9rent, client, quelle est la diff\u00e9rence ?", "titleReword": "diff\u00e9rent client societaire", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 197, "name": "delegues-197", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "delegues"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2958, "body": "\"Un soci\u00e9taire est un client assur\u00e9 \u00e0 la Macif pour ses biens. Un adh\u00e9rent est un client couvert en sant\u00e9-pr\u00e9voyance par Macif-Mutualit\u00e9. Qu\u2019il soit soci\u00e9taire ou adh\u00e9rent, il devient plus qu\u2019un client, c\u2019est un acteur de la gouvernance (il \u00e9lit ses repr\u00e9sentants, choisit le programme d\u2019action mutualiste et peut se porter candidat pour devenir d\u00e9l\u00e9gu\u00e9).\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 197, "name": "delegues-197", "title": "Les d\u00e9l\u00e9gu\u00e9s", "slug": "delegues", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "societaire-adherent-client-quelle-la-difference"}
