{"questionId": 2465, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Quel est le tarif de l'assurance CE/CSE/COS/CAS ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 148, "name": "assurance-vie-148", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "assurance-vie"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2798, "body": "\"Le tarif d\u00e9pend : de votre budget (fonctionnement et \u0153uvre sociale), des biens (mobiliers et immobiliers) que vous souhaitez assurer, le cas \u00e9ch\u00e9ant, du montant de vos valeurs (par exemple : ch\u00e8ques vacances, cadeaux). Le nombre et la nature des activit\u00e9s de votre CE n\u2019ont pas d\u2019influence sur le tarif.<br\\/> Pour en savoir plus n\u2019h\u00e9sitez pas \u00e0 demander votre \u00e9tude personnalis\u00e9e : En ligne, Ou par t\u00e9l\u00e9phone au 09 69 39 49 55 (appel non surtax\u00e9), du lundi au vendredi de 8h30 \u00e0 18h30.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 148, "name": "assurance-vie-148", "title": "Mon assurance vie", "slug": "assurance-vie", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "est-tarif-assurance-ce-cse-cos-cas"}
