{"questionId": 2289, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "LLD hybride ou LLD hybride rechargeable ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 178, "name": "location-longue-duree-hybride-178", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "location-longue-duree-hybride"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2622, "body": "\"En plus des mod\u00e8les v\u00e9hicules hybrides en LLD, vous pouvez d\u00e9sormais choisir une LLD hybride rechargeable. Ces voitures hybrides rechargeables  permettent d\u2019avoir une autonomie plus \u00e9lev\u00e9e, pour rouler plus en \u00e9lectrique. Dans les deux cas, l\u2019avantages de prendre une LLD hybride ou LLD hybride rechargeable avec MACIF C\u2019parti est de toujours rouler dans un v\u00e9hicule neuf, entretenu, assur\u00e9 et assist\u00e9 et de pouvoir changer de v\u00e9hicule \u00e0 la fin de la p\u00e9riode de location pr\u00e9vue.<br\\/>\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 178, "name": "location-longue-duree-hybride-178", "title": "Location Longue Dur\u00e9e Hybride", "slug": "location-longue-duree-hybride", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 1, "questionSlug": "lld-hybride-lld-hybride-rechargeable"}
