{"questionId": 2581, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Qu'est-ce que l'ACS (Aide \u00e0 la Compl\u00e9mentaire Sant\u00e9) ?", "titleReword": "aide mutuelle, aide sant\u00e9", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 216, "name": "booking-com-216", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "booking-com"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2914, "body": "\"En fonction de vos ressources et d'une condition de r\u00e9sidence, vous pouvez b\u00e9n\u00e9ficier de l'Aide \u00e0 la Compl\u00e9mentaire Sant\u00e9, d\u00e9livr\u00e9e par votre Caisse d'assurance maladie. Cette aide financi\u00e8re peut vous permettre d\u2019obtenir de 100 \u00e0 550 euros par personne et par an, montant qui varie selon l'\u00e2ge du b\u00e9n\u00e9ficiaire et la composition de sa famille. Cette somme sera d\u00e9duite de la cotisation annuelle de la compl\u00e9mentaire sant\u00e9 que vous aurez souscrite parmi les contrats s\u00e9lectionn\u00e9s par l'Etat.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 216, "name": "booking-com-216", "title": "Booking.com", "slug": "booking-com", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "title": "Macif Avantages", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "est-ce-lacs-aide-la-complementaire-sante"}
