{"questionId": 2175, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Couvrez-vous ma responsabilit\u00e9 si mon salari\u00e9 ou moi-m\u00eame blesse un client ?", "titleReword": "rc pro, responsabilit\u00e9 pro, resposabilit\u00e9 professionnelle, rc professionnelle", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 56, "name": "professionnels-56", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 299, "name": "activite-professionnelle-299", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "activite-professionnelle"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2508, "body": "\"Oui, votre responsabilit\u00e9 ou celle de vos salari\u00e9s est assur\u00e9e pour les dommages corporels et mat\u00e9riels occasionn\u00e9s \u00e0 un client , dans les conditions et limites fix\u00e9es aux contrats.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 299, "name": "activite-professionnelle-299", "title": "Mon activit\u00e9 professionnelle", "slug": "activite-professionnelle", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 56, "name": "professionnels-56", "title": "Professionnels", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "couvrez-vous-responsabilite-si-salarie-ou-moi-meme-blesse-client"}
