{"questionId": 2426, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Que couvre l'option valeur major\u00e9e du v\u00e9hicule ?", "titleReword": "surc\u00f4te, cotation, cote voiture,majoration voiture", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 236, "name": "hotels-com-236", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "hotels-com"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2759, "body": "\"En cas de destruction totale du v\u00e9hicule r\u00e9sultant d'un \u00e9v\u00e9nement garanti, pendant les 3 ans suivant la date d'achat du v\u00e9hicule neuf, vous b\u00e9n\u00e9ficiez d'une indemnisation correspondant au prix d'acquisition du v\u00e9hicule sans d\u00e9duction de v\u00e9tust\u00e9. Et au-del\u00e0, la valeur de remplacement fix\u00e9e par l'expert est major\u00e9e de : \u2022 30 % pour les voitures \u00e2g\u00e9es de 3 \u00e0 8 ans,<br\\/>\u2022 40 % pour les voitures \u00e2g\u00e9es de plus de 8 ans.  Pour conna\u00eetre le prix de cette option, r\u00e9alisez un devis d'assurance automobile en ligne.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 236, "name": "hotels-com-236", "title": "Hotels.com", "slug": "hotels-com", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "title": "Macif Avantages", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "couvre-option-valeur-majoree-vehicule"}
