{"questionId": 2017, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment obtenir un devis d'assurance auto ?", "titleReword": "devis auto, devis voiture, tarif voiture, tarif auto", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 194, "name": "loisirs-194", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "loisirs"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2350, "body": "\"Pour obtenir un devis d'assurance auto, pensez \u00e0 vous munir de quelques informations  :  date du permis de conduire, coefficient de bonus malus, immatriculation du v\u00e9hicule, date de mise en circulation du v\u00e9hicule.<br\\/>Puis, en quelques minutes sur notre site, r\u00e9alisez un devis d'assurance auto en ligne et obtenez notre meilleur tarif pour votre v\u00e9hicule !\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 194, "name": "loisirs-194", "title": "Mes loisirs", "slug": "loisirs", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 1, "questionSlug": "comment-obtenir-devis-assurance-auto"}
