{"questionId": 2636, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Suis-je bien prot\u00e9g\u00e9(e) si je porte un gilet airbag moto ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 186, "name": "2-roues-186", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "2-roues"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2969, "body": "\"Incontestablement s'\u00e9quiper d'un gilet airbag moto permet en cas de chute de ralentir la vitesse d'un impact, et m\u00eame s'il n'est pas obligatoire, il est essentiel car en prot\u00e9geant les organes vitaux il peut aussi sauver des vies. La Macif propose \u00e0 ses soci\u00e9taires de s'\u00e9quiper \u00e0 moindre co\u00fbt de gilet airbag de qualit\u00e9, filaire ou \u00e9lectronique.<br\\/>Retrouvez nos offres sur Macif Avantages.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 186, "name": "2-roues-186", "title": "Mon 2 roues", "slug": "2-roues", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "suis-je-bien-protege-e-si-porte-gilet-airbag-moto"}
