{"questionId": 2558, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Qu'est ce que aidants / aid\u00e9s ?", "titleReword": "garantie autonomie, aidant, aid\u00e9, handicap, perte d'autonomie, garantie sant\u00e9, immobilisation, hospitalisation, d\u00e9pendance", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 276, "name": "marketplace-276", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "marketplace"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2891, "body": "\"Aidants & Aid\u00e9s est un ensemble de prestations d\u2019assistance, incluses dans les contrats Garantie Autonomie et D\u00e9pendance et Garantie Sant\u00e9*. Ces prestations sont destin\u00e9es \u00e0 soutenir les aidants d\u2019un proche en situation de handicap ou de perte d\u2019autonomie.<br\\/>Elles interviennent \u00e0 des moments cl\u00e9s du parcours de l\u2019aidant avec la personne aid\u00e9e en lui permettant  notamment de : r\u00e9aliser un bilan de sa situation lui apporter une aide administrative dans les d\u00e9marches organiser un relais en cas d\u2019immobilisation \u00e0 domicile ou d\u2019hospitalisation l\u2019 aider \u00e0 l\u2019organisation du r\u00e9pit.  <br\\/> * Dans les conditions et limites du contrat.\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 276, "name": "marketplace-276", "title": "La marketplace", "slug": "marketplace", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 59, "name": "macif-avantages-59", "title": "Macif Avantages", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "est-que-aidants-aides"}
