{"questionId": 2559, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Qu'est ce que la grille AGGIR ?", "titleReword": "grille AGGIR, AGGIR, autonomie, GIR, perte d'autonomie, degr\u00e9 de d\u00e9pendance, allocation personnalis\u00e9e d'autonomie, APA", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 194, "name": "loisirs-194", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "loisirs"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2892, "body": "\"La grille AGGIR (Autonomie G\u00e9rontologique Groupe Iso-Ressources) classe le degr\u00e9 de d\u00e9pendance d\u2019une personne (GIR). Il existe 6 GIR (Groupe Iso-ressource) : le GIR 1 est le niveau de perte d\u2019autonomie le plus fort et le GIR 6 correspond \u00e0 une personne autonome. Le GIR 4 est le premier niveau de perte d'autonomie reconnu par les Pouvoirs Publics qui permet de b\u00e9n\u00e9ficier de l'Allocation Personnalis\u00e9e d'Autonomie (APA).\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 194, "name": "loisirs-194", "title": "Mes loisirs", "slug": "loisirs", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "est-que-grille-aggir"}
