{"questionId": 1908, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment consulter les conditions g\u00e9n\u00e9rales de mon contrat ?", "titleReword": "conditions g\u00e9n\u00e9rales contrat, d\u00e9tail contrat, auto, deux roues, sante, garantie accident, banque, t\u00e9l\u00e9charger conditions g\u00e9n\u00e9rales, police", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 199, "name": "espace-personnel-199", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "espace-personnel"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2241, "body": "\"Pour consulter les conditions g\u00e9n\u00e9rales de votre contrat Macif, il vous suffit simplement de les t\u00e9l\u00e9charger :<br\\/> \u2022 dans la rubrique \\\"Documentation contractuelle\\\" de chaque page produit.<br\\/> <br\\/>Par exemple : <br\\/> - Conditions g\u00e9n\u00e9rales auto           - Conditions g\u00e9n\u00e9rales habitation principale           - Conditions g\u00e9n\u00e9rales moto           - Conditions g\u00e9n\u00e9rales camping-car           - Conditions g\u00e9n\u00e9rales navigation de plaisance<br\\/> <br\\/>\u2022 ou dans la rubrique \\\"D\u00e9tail de votre Contrat\\\" au sein de votre Espace Assurance.<br\\/> Comment me rendre dans mon espace personnel ?\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 199, "name": "espace-personnel-199", "title": "Mon espace personnel", "slug": "espace-personnel", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 1, "questionSlug": "comment-consulter-conditions-generales-mon-contrat"}
