{"questionId": 2532, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Quels sont les diff\u00e9rents r\u00e9gimes de retraite ?", "titleReword": null, "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 61, "name": "site-61", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 150, "name": "credit-auto-150", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-auto"}, {"filterId": 151, "name": "credit-moto-151", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "credit-moto"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2865, "body": "\"Le R\u00e9gime G\u00e9n\u00e9ral : <br\\/>R\u00e9gime de retraite des salari\u00e9s du secteur priv\u00e9, des contractuels de droit public et des artistes auteurs.<br\\/>Au niveau national, le r\u00e9gime g\u00e9n\u00e9ral est g\u00e9r\u00e9 par l\u2019Assurance retraite. (  ) Les R\u00e9gimes Align\u00e9s :<br\\/>Les r\u00e9gimes suivants ont adopt\u00e9 des r\u00e8gles communes pour calculer les droits \u00e0 la retraite :<br\\/>- le r\u00e9gime g\u00e9n\u00e9ral des salari\u00e9s,<br\\/>- le r\u00e9gime des travailleurs ind\u00e9pendants,<br\\/>- le r\u00e9gime des salari\u00e9s agricoles.<br\\/>Ils ont aussi mis en place une demande unique de retraite ; il suffit de d\u00e9poser une demande aupr\u00e8s de l\u2019un d\u2019eux, qui la transmet aux autres. Les R\u00e9gimes sp\u00e9ciaux :<br\\/>R\u00e9gimes de retraite couvrant certaines cat\u00e9gories de salari\u00e9s du secteur public ou parapublic. Exemples : fonctionnaires, agents SNCF, salari\u00e9s de la RATP, etc\u2026\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 150, "name": "credit-auto-150", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Auto", "slug": "credit-auto", "active": "active"}, {"thematicId": 151, "name": "credit-moto-151", "title": "Cr\u00e9dit Moto", "slug": "credit-moto", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 61, "name": "site-61", "title": "Site", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 0, "questionSlug": "sont-differents-regimes-retraite"}
