{"questionId": 1925, "knowledgebaseId": 22, "title": "Comment contacter la Macif pendant le confinement ?", "titleReword": "agence ferm\u00e9e, agence coronavirus, covid-19, covid, fermeture agence, agence macif, agence confinement", "status": "active", "filters": [{"filterId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "type": "tag", "active": "active", "slug": null}, {"filterId": 199, "name": "espace-personnel-199", "type": "thematic", "active": "active", "slug": "espace-personnel"}], "responses": [{"responseId": 2258, "body": "\"Afin de limiter la propagation du coronavirus, la Macif a ferm\u00e9 ses agences pendant la dur\u00e9e du confinement.<br\\/>Dans ce contexte, pour d\u00e9clarer ou suivre un sinistre, g\u00e9rer vos contrats, r\u00e9gler votre \u00e9ch\u00e9ance, consulter vos remboursements, demander une attestation, vous pouvez :  vous connecter \u00e0 votre espace personnel et, le cas \u00e9ch\u00e9ant, \u00e0 votre messagerie, contacter votre conseiller Macif par t\u00e9l\u00e9phone, utiliser l'appli Macif. Nous vous remercions de votre patience et de votre fid\u00e9lit\u00e9, les d\u00e9lais de traitement peuvent \u00eatre allong\u00e9s.\u00bb\"", "channel": "faq", "status": "published"}], "thematics": [{"thematicId": 199, "name": "espace-personnel-199", "title": "Mon espace personnel", "slug": "espace-personnel", "active": "active"}], "tags": [{"tagId": 55, "name": "particuliers-55", "title": "Particuliers", "active": "active"}, {"tagId": 60, "name": "appli-60", "title": "Appli", "active": "active"}], "promoted": false, "frequent": false, "boost": 1, "questionSlug": "comment-contacter-macif-pendant-confinement"}
